1901  /*--- Store the particular global element count in the class data,
1902  and set the class data pointer to the connectivity array. ---*/
1903 
1904  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) {
1905  switch (Elem_Type) {
1906  case LINE:
1907  nGlobal_Line = nElem_Total;
1908  if (nGlobal_Line > 0) Conn_Line = Conn_Elem;
1909  break;
1910  case TRIANGLE:
1911  nGlobal_BoundTria = nElem_Total;
1912  if (nGlobal_BoundTria > 0) Conn_BoundTria = Conn_Elem;
1913  break;
1914  case QUADRILATERAL:
1915  nGlobal_BoundQuad = nElem_Total;
1916  if (nGlobal_BoundQuad > 0) Conn_BoundQuad = Conn_Elem;
1917  break;
1918  default:
1919  cout << "Error: Unrecognized element type \n";
1920  exit(EXIT_FAILURE); break;
1921  }
1922  }
1923 
1924 }
1925 
1926 void COutput::MergeSolution(CConfig *config, CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver, unsigned short val_iZone) {
1927 
1928  unsigned short Kind_Solver = config->GetKind_Solver();
1929  unsigned short iVar = 0, jVar = 0, FirstIndex = NONE, SecondIndex = NONE, ThirdIndex = NONE;
1930  unsigned short nVar_First = 0, nVar_Second = 0, nVar_Third = 0;
1931  unsigned short iVar_GridVel = 0, iVar_PressCp = 0, iVar_Density = 0, iVar_Lam = 0, iVar_MachMean = 0,
1932  iVar_ViscCoeffs = 0, iVar_HeatCoeffs = 0, iVar_Sens = 0, iVar_Extra = 0, iVar_Eddy = 0, iVar_Sharp = 0,
1933  iVar_FEA_Vel = 0, iVar_FEA_Accel = 0, iVar_FEA_Stress = 0, iVar_FEA_Stress_3D = 0,
1934  iVar_FEA_Extra = 0, iVar_SensDim = 0;
1935  unsigned long iPoint = 0, jPoint = 0, iVertex = 0, iMarker = 0;
1936  su2double Gas_Constant, Mach2Vel, Mach_Motion, RefDensity, RefPressure = 0.0, factor = 0.0;
1937 
1938  su2double *Aux_Frict_x = NULL, *Aux_Frict_y = NULL, *Aux_Frict_z = NULL, *Aux_Heat = NULL, *Aux_yPlus = NULL, *Aux_Sens = NULL;
1939 
1940  unsigned short CurrentIndex;
1941  int *Local_Halo;
1942  unsigned long Buffer_Send_nPoint[1], *Buffer_Recv_nPoint = NULL;
1943  unsigned long nLocalPoint = 0, MaxLocalPoint = 0;
1944  unsigned long iGlobal_Index = 0, nBuffer_Scalar = 0;
1945  bool Wrt_Halo = config->GetWrt_Halo(), isPeriodic;
1946 
1947  int iProcessor;
1948  int rank = MASTER_NODE;
1949  int size = SINGLE_NODE;
1950 
1951 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
1952  MPI_Comm_rank(MPI_COMM_WORLD, &rank);
1953  MPI_Comm_size(MPI_COMM_WORLD, &size);
1954 #endif
1955 
1956  bool grid_movement = (config->GetGrid_Movement());
1957  bool compressible = (config->GetKind_Regime() == COMPRESSIBLE);
1958  bool incompressible = (config->GetKind_Regime() == INCOMPRESSIBLE);
1959  bool freesurface = (config->GetKind_Regime() == FREESURFACE);
1960  bool transition = (config->GetKind_Trans_Model() == LM);
1961  bool flow = (( config->GetKind_Solver() == EULER ) ||
1962  ( config->GetKind_Solver() == NAVIER_STOKES ) ||
1963  ( config->GetKind_Solver() == RANS ) ||
1964  ( config->GetKind_Solver() == ADJ_EULER ) ||
1965  ( config->GetKind_Solver() == ADJ_NAVIER_STOKES ) ||
1966  ( config->GetKind_Solver() == ADJ_RANS ) );
1967  bool fem = (config->GetKind_Solver() == FEM_ELASTICITY);
1968 
1969  unsigned short iDim;
1970  unsigned short nDim = geometry->GetnDim();
1971  su2double RefAreaCoeff = config->GetRefAreaCoeff();
1972  su2double Gamma = config->GetGamma();
1973  su2double RefVel2, *Normal, Area;
1974 
1975  /*--- Set the non-dimensionalization ---*/
1976  if (flow) {
1977  if (grid_movement) {
1978  Gas_Constant = config->GetGas_ConstantND();
1979  Mach2Vel = sqrt(Gamma*Gas_Constant*config->GetTemperature_FreeStreamND());
1980  Mach_Motion = config->GetMach_Motion();
1981  RefVel2 = (Mach_Motion*Mach2Vel)*(Mach_Motion*Mach2Vel);
1982  }
1983  else {
1984  RefVel2 = 0.0;
1985  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
1986  RefVel2 += solver[FLOW_SOL]->GetVelocity_Inf(iDim)*solver[FLOW_SOL]->GetVelocity_Inf(iDim);
1987  }
1988  RefDensity = solver[FLOW_SOL]->GetDensity_Inf();
1989  RefPressure = solver[FLOW_SOL]->GetPressure_Inf();
1990  factor = 1.0 / (0.5*RefDensity*RefAreaCoeff*RefVel2);
1991  }
1992 
1993  /*--- Prepare send buffers for the conservative variables. Need to
1994  find the total number of conservative variables and also the
1995  index for their particular solution container. ---*/
1996 
1997  switch (Kind_Solver) {
1998  case EULER : case NAVIER_STOKES: FirstIndex = FLOW_SOL; SecondIndex = NONE; ThirdIndex = NONE; break;
1999  case RANS : FirstIndex = FLOW_SOL; SecondIndex = TURB_SOL; if (transition) ThirdIndex=TRANS_SOL; else ThirdIndex = NONE; break;
2000  case POISSON_EQUATION: FirstIndex = POISSON_SOL; SecondIndex = NONE; ThirdIndex = NONE; break;
2001  case WAVE_EQUATION: FirstIndex = WAVE_SOL; SecondIndex = NONE; ThirdIndex = NONE; break;
2002  case HEAT_EQUATION: FirstIndex = HEAT_SOL; SecondIndex = NONE; ThirdIndex = NONE; break;
2003  case FEM_ELASTICITY: FirstIndex = FEA_SOL; SecondIndex = NONE; ThirdIndex = NONE; break;
2004  case ADJ_EULER : case ADJ_NAVIER_STOKES : FirstIndex = ADJFLOW_SOL; SecondIndex = NONE; ThirdIndex = NONE; break;
2005  case ADJ_RANS : FirstIndex = ADJFLOW_SOL; if (config->GetFrozen_Visc()) SecondIndex = NONE; else SecondIndex = ADJTURB_SOL; ThirdIndex = NONE; break;
2006  case DISC_ADJ_EULER: case DISC_ADJ_NAVIER_STOKES: FirstIndex = ADJFLOW_SOL; SecondIndex = NONE; ThirdIndex = NONE; break;
2007  case DISC_ADJ_RANS: FirstIndex = ADJFLOW_SOL; SecondIndex = ADJTURB_SOL; ThirdIndex = NONE; break;
2008  default: SecondIndex = NONE; ThirdIndex = NONE; break;
2009  }
2010 
2011  nVar_First = solver[FirstIndex]->GetnVar();
2012  if (SecondIndex != NONE) nVar_Second = solver[SecondIndex]->GetnVar();
2013  if (ThirdIndex != NONE) nVar_Third = solver[ThirdIndex]->GetnVar();
2014  nVar_Consv = nVar_First + nVar_Second + nVar_Third;
2015  nVar_Total = nVar_Consv;
2016 
2017  if (!config->GetLow_MemoryOutput()) {
2018 
2019  /*--- Add the limiters ---*/
2020 
2021  if (config->GetWrt_Limiters()) nVar_Total += nVar_Consv;
2022 
2023  /*--- Add the residuals ---*/
2024 
2025  if (config->GetWrt_Residuals()) nVar_Total += nVar_Consv;
2026 
2027  /*--- Add the grid velocity to the restart file for the unsteady adjoint ---*/
2028 
2029  if (grid_movement && !fem) {
2030  iVar_GridVel = nVar_Total;
2031  if (geometry->GetnDim() == 2) nVar_Total += 2;
2032  else if (geometry->GetnDim() == 3) nVar_Total += 3;
2033  }
2034 
2035  /*--- Add density to the restart file ---*/
2036 
2037  if ((config->GetKind_Regime() == FREESURFACE)) {
2038  iVar_Density = nVar_Total; nVar_Total += 1;
2039  }
2040 
2041  /*--- Add Pressure, Temperature, Cp, Mach to the restart file ---*/
2042 
2043  if ((Kind_Solver == EULER) || (Kind_Solver == NAVIER_STOKES) || (Kind_Solver == RANS)) {
2044  iVar_PressCp = nVar_Total; nVar_Total += 3;
2045  iVar_MachMean = nVar_Total; nVar_Total += 1;
2046  }
2047 
2048  /*--- Add Laminar Viscosity, Skin Friction, Heat Flux, & yPlus to the restart file ---*/
2049 
2050  if ((Kind_Solver == NAVIER_STOKES) || (Kind_Solver == RANS)) {
2051  iVar_Lam = nVar_Total;
2052  nVar_Total += 1;
2053  iVar_ViscCoeffs = nVar_Total;
2054  if (geometry->GetnDim() == 2) nVar_Total += 2;
2055  else if (geometry->GetnDim() == 3) nVar_Total += 3;
2056  iVar_HeatCoeffs = nVar_Total;
2057  nVar_Total += 2;
2058  }
2059 
2060  /*--- Add Eddy Viscosity to the restart file ---*/
2061 
2062  if (Kind_Solver == RANS) {
2063  iVar_Eddy = nVar_Total; nVar_Total += 1;
2064  }
2065 
2066  /*--- Add Sharp edges to the restart file ---*/
2067 
2068  if (config->GetWrt_SharpEdges()) {
2069  if ((Kind_Solver == EULER) || (Kind_Solver == NAVIER_STOKES) || (Kind_Solver == RANS)) {
2070  iVar_Sharp = nVar_Total; nVar_Total += 1;
2071  }
2072  }
2073 
2074  //if (Kind_Solver == POISSON_EQUATION) {
2075  // iVar_EF = nVar_Total; nVar_Total += geometry->GetnDim();
2076  //}
2077 
2078  if (( Kind_Solver == ADJ_EULER ) || ( Kind_Solver == ADJ_NAVIER_STOKES ) ||
2079  ( Kind_Solver == ADJ_RANS )) {
2080  iVar_Sens = nVar_Total; nVar_Total += 2;
2081  }
2082 
2083  if (Kind_Solver == FEM_ELASTICITY) {
2084  /*--- If the analysis is dynamic... ---*/
2085  if (config->GetDynamic_Analysis() == DYNAMIC){
2086  /*--- Velocities ---*/
2087  iVar_FEA_Vel = nVar_Total;
2088  if (geometry->GetnDim() == 2) nVar_Total += 2;
2089  else if (geometry->GetnDim() == 3) nVar_Total += 3;
2090  /*--- Accelerations ---*/
2091  iVar_FEA_Accel = nVar_Total;
2092  if (geometry->GetnDim() == 2) nVar_Total += 2;
2093  else if (geometry->GetnDim() == 3) nVar_Total += 3;
2094  }
2095  iVar_FEA_Stress = nVar_Total; nVar_Total += 3;
2096  if (geometry->GetnDim() == 3) {iVar_FEA_Stress_3D = nVar_Total; nVar_Total += 3;}
2097  iVar_FEA_Extra = nVar_Total; nVar_Total += 1;
2098  }
2099 
2100  if ((Kind_Solver == DISC_ADJ_EULER) ||
2101  (Kind_Solver == DISC_ADJ_NAVIER_STOKES) ||
2102  (Kind_Solver == DISC_ADJ_RANS)){
2103  iVar_Sens = nVar_Total; nVar_Total += 1;
2104  iVar_SensDim = nVar_Total; nVar_Total += nDim;
2105  }
2106 
2107  if (config->GetExtraOutput()) {
2108  if (Kind_Solver == RANS) {
2109  iVar_Extra = nVar_Total; nVar_Extra = solver[TURB_SOL]->GetnOutputVariables(); nVar_Total += nVar_Extra;
2110  }
2111  }
2112 
2113  }
2114 
2115  Local_Halo = new int[geometry->GetnPoint()];
2116  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < geometry->GetnPoint(); iPoint++)
2117  Local_Halo[iPoint] = !geometry->node[iPoint]->GetDomain();
2118 
2119  /*--- Search all send/recv boundaries on this partition for any periodic
2120  nodes that were part of the original domain. We want to recover these
2121  for visualization purposes. ---*/
2122 
2123  if (Wrt_Halo) {
2124  nLocalPoint = geometry->GetnPoint();
2125  } else {
2126  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
2127  if (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == SEND_RECEIVE) {
2128 
2129  /*--- Checking for less than or equal to the rank, because there may
2130  be some periodic halo nodes that send info to the same rank. ---*/
2131 
2132  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
2133  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
2134  isPeriodic = ((geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetRotation_Type() > 0) &&
2135  (geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetRotation_Type() % 2 == 1));
2136  if (isPeriodic) Local_Halo[iPoint] = false;
2137  }
2138  }
2139  }
2140 
2141  /*--- Sum total number of nodes that belong to the domain ---*/
2142 
2143  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < geometry->GetnPoint(); iPoint++)
2144  if (Local_Halo[iPoint] == false)
2145  nLocalPoint++;
2146 
2147  }
2148  Buffer_Send_nPoint[0] = nLocalPoint;
2149 
2150  /*--- Each processor sends its local number of nodes to the master. ---*/
2151 
2152  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) Buffer_Recv_nPoint = new unsigned long[size];
2153 
2154 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
2155  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&nLocalPoint, &MaxLocalPoint, 1, MPI_UNSIGNED_LONG, MPI_MAX, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
2156  SU2_MPI::Gather(&Buffer_Send_nPoint, 1, MPI_UNSIGNED_LONG, Buffer_Recv_nPoint, 1, MPI_UNSIGNED_LONG, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
2157 #else
2158  MaxLocalPoint = nLocalPoint;
2159  Buffer_Recv_nPoint[0] = Buffer_Send_nPoint[0];
2160 #endif
2161 
2162  nBuffer_Scalar = MaxLocalPoint;
2163 
2164  /*--- Send and Recv buffers. ---*/
2165 
2166  su2double *Buffer_Send_Var = new su2double[MaxLocalPoint];
2167  su2double *Buffer_Recv_Var = NULL;
2168 
2169  su2double *Buffer_Send_Res = new su2double[MaxLocalPoint];
2170  su2double *Buffer_Recv_Res = NULL;
2171 
2172  su2double *Buffer_Send_Vol = new su2double[MaxLocalPoint];
2173  su2double *Buffer_Recv_Vol = NULL;
2174 
2175  unsigned long *Buffer_Send_GlobalIndex = new unsigned long[MaxLocalPoint];
2176  unsigned long *Buffer_Recv_GlobalIndex = NULL;
2177 
2178  /*--- Auxiliary vectors for surface coefficients ---*/
2179 
2180  if ((Kind_Solver == NAVIER_STOKES) || (Kind_Solver == RANS)) {
2181  Aux_Frict_x = new su2double[geometry->GetnPoint()];
2182  Aux_Frict_y = new su2double[geometry->GetnPoint()];
2183  Aux_Frict_z = new su2double[geometry->GetnPoint()];
2184  Aux_Heat = new su2double[geometry->GetnPoint()];
2185  Aux_yPlus = new su2double[geometry->GetnPoint()];
2186  }
2187 
2188  if ((Kind_Solver == ADJ_EULER) ||
2189  (Kind_Solver == ADJ_NAVIER_STOKES) ||
2190  (Kind_Solver == ADJ_RANS) ||
2191  (Kind_Solver == DISC_ADJ_EULER) ||
2192  (Kind_Solver == DISC_ADJ_NAVIER_STOKES) ||
2193  (Kind_Solver == DISC_ADJ_RANS)) {
2194  Aux_Sens = new su2double[geometry->GetnPoint()];
2195  }
2196 
2197  /*--- Prepare the receive buffers in the master node only. ---*/
2198 
2199  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) {
2200 
2201  Buffer_Recv_Var = new su2double[size*MaxLocalPoint];
2202  Buffer_Recv_Res = new su2double[size*MaxLocalPoint];
2203  Buffer_Recv_Vol = new su2double[size*MaxLocalPoint];
2204  Buffer_Recv_GlobalIndex = new unsigned long[size*MaxLocalPoint];
2205 
2206  /*--- Sum total number of nodes to be written and allocate arrays ---*/
2207  nGlobal_Poin = 0;
2208  for (iProcessor = 0; iProcessor < size; iProcessor++) {
2209  nGlobal_Poin += Buffer_Recv_nPoint[iProcessor];
2210  }
2211  Data = new su2double*[nVar_Total];
2212  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar_Total; iVar++) {
2213  Data[iVar] = new su2double[nGlobal_Poin];
2214  }
2215  }
2216 
2217  /*--- Main communication routine. Loop over each variable that has
2218  been requested by the user and perform the MPI comm. Temporary
2219  1-D buffers are used to send the solution for each variable at all
2220  nodes on each partition to the master node. These are then unpacked
2221  by the master and sorted by global index in one large n-dim. array. ---*/
2222 
2223  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar_Consv; iVar++) {
2224 
2225  /*--- Logic for which solution class to draw from. ---*/
2226 
2227  jVar = iVar;
2228  CurrentIndex = FirstIndex;
2229  if ((SecondIndex != NONE) && (iVar > nVar_First-1)) {
2230  jVar = iVar - nVar_First;
2231  CurrentIndex = SecondIndex;
2232  }
2233  if ((SecondIndex != NONE) && (ThirdIndex != NONE) && (iVar > (nVar_First + nVar_Second-1))) {
2234  jVar = iVar - nVar_First - nVar_Second;
2235  CurrentIndex = ThirdIndex;
2236  }
2237 
2238  /*--- Loop over this partition to collect the current variable ---*/
2239 
2240  jPoint = 0;
2241  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < geometry->GetnPoint(); iPoint++) {
2242 
2243  /*--- Check for halos & write only if requested ---*/
2244 
2245  if (!Local_Halo[iPoint] || Wrt_Halo) {
2246 
2247  /*--- Get this variable into the temporary send buffer. ---*/
2248 
2249  Buffer_Send_Var[jPoint] = solver[CurrentIndex]->node[iPoint]->GetSolution(jVar);
2250 
2251  if (!config->GetLow_MemoryOutput()) {
2252 
2253  if (config->GetWrt_Limiters()) {
2254  Buffer_Send_Vol[jPoint] = solver[CurrentIndex]->node[iPoint]->GetLimiter_Primitive(jVar);
2255  }
2256 
2257  if (config->GetWrt_Residuals()) {
2258  if (!config->GetDiscrete_Adjoint()){
2259  Buffer_Send_Res[jPoint] = solver[CurrentIndex]->LinSysRes.GetBlock(iPoint, jVar);
2260  } else {
2261  Buffer_Send_Res[jPoint] = solver[CurrentIndex]->node[iPoint]->GetSolution(jVar) -
2262  solver[CurrentIndex]->node[iPoint]->GetSolution_Old(jVar);
2263  }
2264  }
2265 
2266  }
2267 
2268  /*--- Only send/recv the volumes & global indices during the first loop ---*/
2269 
2270  if (iVar == 0) {
2271  Buffer_Send_GlobalIndex[jPoint] = geometry->node[iPoint]->GetGlobalIndex();
2272  }
2273 
2274  jPoint++;
2275 
2276  }
2277  }
2278 
2279  /*--- Gather the data on the master node. ---*/
2280 
2281 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
2282  SU2_MPI::Gather(Buffer_Send_Var, nBuffer_Scalar, MPI_DOUBLE, Buffer_Recv_Var, nBuffer_Scalar, MPI_DOUBLE, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
2283 #else
2284  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nBuffer_Scalar; iPoint++) Buffer_Recv_Var[iPoint] = Buffer_Send_Var[iPoint];
2285 #endif
2286  if (!config->GetLow_MemoryOutput()) {
2287 
2288  if (config->GetWrt_Limiters()) {
2289 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
2290  SU2_MPI::Gather(Buffer_Send_Vol, nBuffer_Scalar, MPI_DOUBLE, Buffer_Recv_Vol, nBuffer_Scalar, MPI_DOUBLE, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
2291 #else
2292  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nBuffer_Scalar; iPoint++) Buffer_Recv_Vol[iPoint] = Buffer_Send_Vol[iPoint];
2293 #endif
2294  }
2295 
2296  if (config->GetWrt_Residuals()) {
2297 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
2298  SU2_MPI::Gather(Buffer_Send_Res, nBuffer_Scalar, MPI_DOUBLE, Buffer_Recv_Res, nBuffer_Scalar, MPI_DOUBLE, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
2299 #else
2300  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nBuffer_Scalar; iPoint++) Buffer_Recv_Res[iPoint] = Buffer_Send_Res[iPoint];
2301 #endif
2302  }
2303 
2304  }
2305 
2306  if (iVar == 0) {
2307 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
2308  SU2_MPI::Gather(Buffer_Send_GlobalIndex, nBuffer_Scalar, MPI_UNSIGNED_LONG, Buffer_Recv_GlobalIndex, nBuffer_Scalar, MPI_UNSIGNED_LONG, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
2309 #else
2310  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nBuffer_Scalar; iPoint++) Buffer_Recv_GlobalIndex[iPoint] = Buffer_Send_GlobalIndex[iPoint];
2311 #endif
2312  }
2313 
2314  /*--- The master node unpacks and sorts this variable by global index ---*/
2315 
2316  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) {
2317  jPoint = 0;
2318  for (iProcessor = 0; iProcessor < size; iProcessor++) {
2319  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < Buffer_Recv_nPoint[iProcessor]; iPoint++) {
2320 
2321  /*--- Get global index, then loop over each variable and store ---*/
2322 
2323  iGlobal_Index = Buffer_Recv_GlobalIndex[jPoint];
2324 
2325  Data[iVar][iGlobal_Index] = Buffer_Recv_Var[jPoint];
2326 
2327  if (!config->GetLow_MemoryOutput()) {
2328 
2329  if (config->GetWrt_Limiters()) {
2330  Data[iVar+nVar_Consv][iGlobal_Index] = Buffer_Recv_Vol[jPoint];
2331  }
2332 
2333  if (config->GetWrt_Residuals()) {
2334  unsigned short ExtraIndex;
2335  ExtraIndex = nVar_Consv;
2336  if (config->GetWrt_Limiters()) ExtraIndex = 2*nVar_Consv;
2337  Data[iVar+ExtraIndex][iGlobal_Index] = Buffer_Recv_Res[jPoint];
2338  }
2339 
2340  }
2341 
2342  jPoint++;
2343  }
2344  /*--- Adjust jPoint to index of next proc's data in the buffers. ---*/
2345  jPoint = (iProcessor+1)*nBuffer_Scalar;
2346  }
2347  }
2348 
2349  }
2350 
2351  if (!config->GetLow_MemoryOutput()) {
2352 
2353  /*--- Additional communication routine for the grid velocity. Note that
2354  we are reusing the same temporary buffers from above for efficiency.
2355  Also, in the future more routines like this could be used to write
2356  an arbitrary number of additional variables to the file. ---*/
2357 
2358  if (grid_movement && !fem) {
2359 
2360  /*--- Loop over this partition to collect the current variable ---*/
2361 
2362  jPoint = 0; su2double *Grid_Vel;
2363  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < geometry->GetnPoint(); iPoint++) {
2364 
2365  /*--- Check for halos & write only if requested ---*/
2366 
2367  if (!Local_Halo[iPoint] || Wrt_Halo) {
2368 
2369  /*--- Load buffers with the three grid velocity components. ---*/
2370 
2371  Grid_Vel = geometry->node[iPoint]->GetGridVel();
2372  Buffer_Send_Var[jPoint] = Grid_Vel[0];
2373  Buffer_Send_Res[jPoint] = Grid_Vel[1];
2374  if (geometry->GetnDim() == 3) Buffer_Send_Vol[jPoint] = Grid_Vel[2];
2375  jPoint++;
2376  }
2377  }
2378 
2379  /*--- Gather the data on the master node. ---*/
2380 
2381 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
2382  SU2_MPI::Gather(Buffer_Send_Var, nBuffer_Scalar, MPI_DOUBLE, Buffer_Recv_Var, nBuffer_Scalar, MPI_DOUBLE, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
2383  SU2_MPI::Gather(Buffer_Send_Res, nBuffer_Scalar, MPI_DOUBLE, Buffer_Recv_Res, nBuffer_Scalar, MPI_DOUBLE, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
2384  if (geometry->GetnDim() == 3) {
2385  SU2_MPI::Gather(Buffer_Send_Vol, nBuffer_Scalar, MPI_DOUBLE, Buffer_Recv_Vol, nBuffer_Scalar, MPI_DOUBLE, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
2386  }
2387 #else
2388  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nBuffer_Scalar; iPoint++) Buffer_Recv_Var[iPoint] = Buffer_Send_Var[iPoint];
2389  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nBuffer_Scalar; iPoint++) Buffer_Recv_Res[iPoint] = Buffer_Send_Res[iPoint];
2390  if (geometry->GetnDim() == 3) {
2391  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nBuffer_Scalar; iPoint++) Buffer_Recv_Vol[iPoint] = Buffer_Send_Vol[iPoint];
2392  }
2393 #endif
2394 
2395  /*--- The master node unpacks and sorts this variable by global index ---*/
2396 
2397  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) {
2398  jPoint = 0; iVar = iVar_GridVel;
2399  for (iProcessor = 0; iProcessor < size; iProcessor++) {
2400  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < Buffer_Recv_nPoint[iProcessor]; iPoint++) {
2401 
2402  /*--- Get global index, then loop over each variable and store ---*/
2403 
2404  iGlobal_Index = Buffer_Recv_GlobalIndex[jPoint];
2405  Data[iVar][iGlobal_Index] = Buffer_Recv_Var[jPoint];
2406  Data[iVar+1][iGlobal_Index] = Buffer_Recv_Res[jPoint];
2407  if (geometry->GetnDim() == 3)
2408  Data[iVar+2][iGlobal_Index] = Buffer_Recv_Vol[jPoint];
2409  jPoint++;
2410  }
2411 
2412  /*--- Adjust jPoint to index of next proc's data in the buffers. ---*/
2413 
2414  jPoint = (iProcessor+1)*nBuffer_Scalar;
2415  }
2416  }
2417  }
2418 
2419  /*--- Communicate the Density in Free-surface problems ---*/
2420 
2421  if (config->GetKind_Regime() == FREESURFACE) {
2422 
2423  /*--- Loop over this partition to collect the current variable ---*/
2424 
2425  jPoint = 0;
2426  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < geometry->GetnPoint(); iPoint++) {
2427 
2428  /*--- Check for halos & write only if requested ---*/
2429 
2430  if (!Local_Halo[iPoint] || Wrt_Halo) {
2431 
2432  /*--- Load buffers with the pressure and mach variables. ---*/
2433  Buffer_Send_Var[jPoint] = solver[FLOW_SOL]->node[iPoint]->GetDensityInc();
2434  jPoint++;
2435  }
2436  }
2437 
2438  /*--- Gather the data on the master node. ---*/
2439 
2440 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
2441  SU2_MPI::Gather(Buffer_Send_Var, nBuffer_Scalar, MPI_DOUBLE, Buffer_Recv_Var, nBuffer_Scalar, MPI_DOUBLE, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
2442 #else
2443  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nBuffer_Scalar; iPoint++) Buffer_Recv_Var[iPoint] = Buffer_Send_Var[iPoint];
2444 #endif
2445 
2446  /*--- The master node unpacks and sorts this variable by global index ---*/
2447 
2448  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) {
2449  jPoint = 0; iVar = iVar_Density;
2450  for (iProcessor = 0; iProcessor < size; iProcessor++) {
2451  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < Buffer_Recv_nPoint[iProcessor]; iPoint++) {
2452 
2453  /*--- Get global index, then loop over each variable and store ---*/
2454 
2455  iGlobal_Index = Buffer_Recv_GlobalIndex[jPoint];
2456  Data[iVar][iGlobal_Index] = Buffer_Recv_Var[jPoint];
2457  jPoint++;
2458  }
2459  /*--- Adjust jPoint to index of next proc's data in the buffers. ---*/
2460 
2461  jPoint = (iProcessor+1)*nBuffer_Scalar;
2462  }
2463  }
2464 
2465  }
2466 
2467  /*--- Communicate Pressure, Cp, and Mach ---*/
2468 
2469  if ((Kind_Solver == EULER) || (Kind_Solver == NAVIER_STOKES) || (Kind_Solver == RANS)) {
2470 
2471  /*--- First, loop through the mesh in order to find and store the
2472  value of the coefficient of pressure at any surface nodes. They
2473  will be placed in an auxiliary vector and then communicated like
2474  all other volumetric variables. ---*/
2475 
2476  /*--- Loop over this partition to collect the current variable ---*/
2477 
2478  jPoint = 0;
2479  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < geometry->GetnPoint(); iPoint++) {
2480 
2481  /*--- Check for halos & write only if requested ---*/
2482 
2483  if (!Local_Halo[iPoint] || Wrt_Halo) {
2484 
2485  /*--- Load buffers with the pressure, Cp, and mach variables. ---*/
2486 
2487  if (compressible) {
2488  Buffer_Send_Var[jPoint] = solver[FLOW_SOL]->node[iPoint]->GetPressure();
2489  Buffer_Send_Res[jPoint] = solver[FLOW_SOL]->node[iPoint]->GetTemperature();
2490  Buffer_Send_Vol[jPoint] = (solver[FLOW_SOL]->node[iPoint]->GetPressure() - RefPressure)*factor*RefAreaCoeff;
2491  }
2492  if (incompressible || freesurface) {
2493  Buffer_Send_Var[jPoint] = solver[FLOW_SOL]->node[iPoint]->GetPressureInc();
2494  Buffer_Send_Res[jPoint] = 0.0;
2495  Buffer_Send_Vol[jPoint] = (solver[FLOW_SOL]->node[iPoint]->GetPressureInc() - RefPressure)*factor*RefAreaCoeff;
2496  }
2497  jPoint++;
2498  }
2499  }
2500 
2501  /*--- Gather the data on the master node. ---*/
2502 
2503 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
2504  SU2_MPI::Gather(Buffer_Send_Var, nBuffer_Scalar, MPI_DOUBLE, Buffer_Recv_Var, nBuffer_Scalar, MPI_DOUBLE, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
2505  SU2_MPI::Gather(Buffer_Send_Res, nBuffer_Scalar, MPI_DOUBLE, Buffer_Recv_Res, nBuffer_Scalar, MPI_DOUBLE, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
2506  SU2_MPI::Gather(Buffer_Send_Vol, nBuffer_Scalar, MPI_DOUBLE, Buffer_Recv_Vol, nBuffer_Scalar, MPI_DOUBLE, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
2507 #else
2508  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nBuffer_Scalar; iPoint++) Buffer_Recv_Var[iPoint] = Buffer_Send_Var[iPoint];
2509  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nBuffer_Scalar; iPoint++) Buffer_Recv_Res[iPoint] = Buffer_Send_Res[iPoint];
2510  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nBuffer_Scalar; iPoint++) Buffer_Recv_Vol[iPoint] = Buffer_Send_Vol[iPoint];
2511 #endif
2512 
2513  /*--- The master node unpacks and sorts this variable by global index ---*/
2514 
2515  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) {
2516  jPoint = 0; iVar = iVar_PressCp;
2517  for (iProcessor = 0; iProcessor < size; iProcessor++) {
2518  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < Buffer_Recv_nPoint[iProcessor]; iPoint++) {
2519 
2520  /*--- Get global index, then loop over each variable and store ---*/
2521 
2522  iGlobal_Index = Buffer_Recv_GlobalIndex[jPoint];
2523  Data[iVar][iGlobal_Index] = Buffer_Recv_Var[jPoint];
2524  Data[iVar+1][iGlobal_Index] = Buffer_Recv_Res[jPoint];
2525  Data[iVar+2][iGlobal_Index] = Buffer_Recv_Vol[jPoint];
2526  jPoint++;
2527  }
2528 
2529  /*--- Adjust jPoint to index of next proc's data in the buffers. ---*/
2530 
2531  jPoint = (iProcessor+1)*nBuffer_Scalar;
2532  }
2533  }
2534  }
2535 
2536  /*--- Communicate Mach---*/
2537 
2538  if ((Kind_Solver == EULER) || (Kind_Solver == NAVIER_STOKES) || (Kind_Solver == RANS)) {
2539 
2540  /*--- Loop over this partition to collect the current variable ---*/
2541 
2542  jPoint = 0;
2543  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < geometry->GetnPoint(); iPoint++) {
2544 
2545  /*--- Check for halos & write only if requested ---*/
2546 
2547  if (!Local_Halo[iPoint] || Wrt_Halo) {
2548 
2549  /*--- Load buffers with the temperature and laminar viscosity variables. ---*/
2550 
2551  if (compressible) {
2552  Buffer_Send_Var[jPoint] = sqrt(solver[FLOW_SOL]->node[iPoint]->GetVelocity2())/
2553  solver[FLOW_SOL]->node[iPoint]->GetSoundSpeed();
2554  }
2555  if (incompressible || freesurface) {
2556  Buffer_Send_Var[jPoint] = sqrt(solver[FLOW_SOL]->node[iPoint]->GetVelocity2())*config->GetVelocity_Ref()/
2557  sqrt(config->GetBulk_Modulus()/(solver[FLOW_SOL]->node[iPoint]->GetDensityInc()*config->GetDensity_Ref()));
2558  }
2559  jPoint++;
2560  }
2561  }
2562 
2563  /*--- Gather the data on the master node. ---*/
2564 
2565 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
2566  SU2_MPI::Gather(Buffer_Send_Var, nBuffer_Scalar, MPI_DOUBLE, Buffer_Recv_Var, nBuffer_Scalar, MPI_DOUBLE, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
2567 #else
2568  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nBuffer_Scalar; iPoint++) Buffer_Recv_Var[iPoint] = Buffer_Send_Var[iPoint];
2569 #endif
2570 
2571  /*--- The master node unpacks and sorts this variable by global index ---*/
2572 
2573  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) {
2574  jPoint = 0; iVar = iVar_MachMean;
2575  for (iProcessor = 0; iProcessor < size; iProcessor++) {
2576  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < Buffer_Recv_nPoint[iProcessor]; iPoint++) {
2577 
2578  /*--- Get global index, then loop over each variable and store ---*/
2579 
2580  iGlobal_Index = Buffer_Recv_GlobalIndex[jPoint];
2581  Data[iVar][iGlobal_Index] = Buffer_Recv_Var[jPoint];
2582  jPoint++;
2583  }
2584 
2585  /*--- Adjust jPoint to index of next proc's data in the buffers. ---*/
2586 
2587  jPoint = (iProcessor+1)*nBuffer_Scalar;
2588  }
2589  }
2590  }
2591

2593

2595 
2596  /*--- Loop over this partition to collect the current variable ---*/
2597 
2598  jPoint = 0;
2599  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < geometry->GetnPoint(); iPoint++) {
2600 
2601  /*--- Check for halos & write only if requested ---*/
2602

2609  }

2623 #endif

2641  jPoint = (iProcessor+1)*nBuffer_Scalar;

2645  /*--- Communicate skin friction ---*/
2646 
2647  /*--- First, loop through the mesh in order to find and store the
2648  value of the viscous coefficients at any surface nodes. They
2649  will be placed in an auxiliary vector and then communicated like
2650  all other volumetric variables. ---*/
2651 
2652  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < geometry->GetnPoint(); iPoint++) {
2653  Aux_Frict_x[iPoint] = 0.0;
2654  Aux_Frict_y[iPoint] = 0.0;
2655  Aux_Frict_z[iPoint] = 0.0;
2656  }
2657  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++)
2658  if (config->GetMarker_All_Plotting(iMarker) == YES) {
2659  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
2660  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
2661  Aux_Frict_x[iPoint] = solver[FLOW_SOL]->GetCSkinFriction(iMarker, iVertex, 0);
2662  Aux_Frict_y[iPoint] = solver[FLOW_SOL]->GetCSkinFriction(iMarker, iVertex, 1);
2663  if (geometry->GetnDim() == 3) Aux_Frict_z[iPoint] = solver[FLOW_SOL]->GetCSkinFriction(iMarker, iVertex, 2);
2664  }
2665  }
2666 
2667  /*--- Loop over this partition to collect the current variable ---*/
2668 
2669  jPoint = 0;
2670  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < geometry->GetnPoint(); iPoint++) {
2671 
2672  /*--- Check for halos & write only if requested ---*/
2673 
2674  if (!Local_Halo[iPoint] || Wrt_Halo) {
2675 
2676  /*--- Load buffers with the three grid velocity components. ---*/
2677 
2678  Buffer_Send_Var[jPoint] = Aux_Frict_x[iPoint];
2679  Buffer_Send_Res[jPoint] = Aux_Frict_y[iPoint];
2680  if (geometry->GetnDim() == 3)
2681  Buffer_Send_Vol[jPoint] = Aux_Frict_z[iPoint];
2682  jPoint++;
2683  }
2684  }
2685 
2686  /*--- Gather the data on the master node. ---*/
2687 
2688 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
2689  SU2_MPI::Gather(Buffer_Send_Var, nBuffer_Scalar, MPI_DOUBLE, Buffer_Recv_Var, nBuffer_Scalar, MPI_DOUBLE, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
2690  SU2_MPI::Gather(Buffer_Send_Res, nBuffer_Scalar, MPI_DOUBLE, Buffer_Recv_Res, nBuffer_Scalar, MPI_DOUBLE, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
2691  if (geometry->GetnDim() == 3) {
2692  SU2_MPI::Gather(Buffer_Send_Vol, nBuffer_Scalar, MPI_DOUBLE, Buffer_Recv_Vol, nBuffer_Scalar, MPI_DOUBLE, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
2693  }
2694 #else
2695  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nBuffer_Scalar; iPoint++)
2696  Buffer_Recv_Var[iPoint] = Buffer_Send_Var[iPoint];
2697  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nBuffer_Scalar; iPoint++)
2698  Buffer_Recv_Res[iPoint] = Buffer_Send_Res[iPoint];
2699  if (geometry->GetnDim() == 3) {
2700  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nBuffer_Scalar; iPoint++)
2701  Buffer_Recv_Vol[iPoint] = Buffer_Send_Vol[iPoint];
2702  }
2703 #endif
2704 
2705  /*--- The master node unpacks and sorts this variable by global index ---*/
2706 
2707  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) {
2708  jPoint = 0;
2709  iVar = iVar_ViscCoeffs;
2710  for (iProcessor = 0; iProcessor < size; iProcessor++) {
2711  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < Buffer_Recv_nPoint[iProcessor]; iPoint++) {
2712 
2713  /*--- Get global index, then loop over each variable and store ---*/
2714 
2715  iGlobal_Index = Buffer_Recv_GlobalIndex[jPoint];
2716  Data[iVar][iGlobal_Index] = Buffer_Recv_Var[jPoint];
2717  Data[iVar + 1][iGlobal_Index] = Buffer_Recv_Res[jPoint];
2718  if (geometry->GetnDim() == 3)
2719  Data[iVar + 2][iGlobal_Index] = Buffer_Recv_Vol[jPoint];
2720  jPoint++;
2721  }
2722

2724

2726  }

2738  Aux_yPlus[iPoint] = 0.0;

2741  if (config->GetMarker_All_Plotting(iMarker) == YES) {

2744  Aux_Heat[iPoint] = solver[FLOW_SOL]->GetHeatFlux(iMarker, iVertex);
2745  Aux_yPlus[iPoint] = solver[FLOW_SOL]->GetYPlus(iMarker, iVertex);
2746  }

2762  Buffer_Send_Vol[jPoint] = Aux_yPlus[iPoint];

2776  SU2_MPI::Gather(Buffer_Send_Vol, nBuffer_Scalar, MPI_DOUBLE, Buffer_Recv_Vol, nBuffer_Scalar, MPI_DOUBLE, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
2777 #else

2779  Buffer_Recv_Res[iPoint] = Buffer_Send_Res[iPoint];

2781  Buffer_Recv_Vol[iPoint] = Buffer_Send_Vol[iPoint];

2915  /*--- Communicate the surface sensitivity ---*/
2916 
2917  if ((Kind_Solver == ADJ_EULER) ||
2918  (Kind_Solver == ADJ_NAVIER_STOKES) ||
2919  (Kind_Solver == ADJ_RANS) ||
2920  (Kind_Solver == DISC_ADJ_EULER) ||
2921  (Kind_Solver == DISC_ADJ_NAVIER_STOKES) ||
2922  (Kind_Solver == DISC_ADJ_RANS)) {
2923 
2924  /*--- First, loop through the mesh in order to find and store the
2925  value of the surface sensitivity at any surface nodes. They
2926  will be placed in an auxiliary vector and then communicated like
2927  all other volumetric variables. ---*/
2928 
2929  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < geometry->GetnPoint(); iPoint++) Aux_Sens[iPoint] = 0.0;
2930  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++)
2931  if (config->GetMarker_All_Plotting(iMarker) == YES) {
2932  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
2933  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
2934  Normal = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal();
2935  Area = 0.0;
2936  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Area += Normal[iDim]*Normal[iDim];
2937  Area = sqrt (Area);
2938  Aux_Sens[iPoint] = solver[ADJFLOW_SOL]->GetCSensitivity(iMarker, iVertex)/Area;
2939  }
2940  }
2941 
2942  /*--- Loop over this partition to collect the current variable ---*/
2943 
2944  jPoint = 0;
2945  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < geometry->GetnPoint(); iPoint++) {
2946 
2947  /*--- Check for halos & write only if requested ---*/
2948 
2949  if (!Local_Halo[iPoint] || Wrt_Halo) {
2950 
2951  /*--- Load buffers with the skin friction, heat transfer, y+ variables. ---*/
2952 
2953  Buffer_Send_Var[jPoint] = Aux_Sens[iPoint];
2954  if ((config->GetKind_ConvNumScheme() == SPACE_CENTERED) && (!config->GetDiscrete_Adjoint()))
2955  Buffer_Send_Res[jPoint] = solver[ADJFLOW_SOL]->node[iPoint]->GetSensor(iPoint);
2956  if ((config->GetKind_ConvNumScheme() == SPACE_UPWIND) && (!config->GetDiscrete_Adjoint()))
2957  Buffer_Send_Res[jPoint] = solver[ADJFLOW_SOL]->node[iPoint]->GetLimiter(0);
2958 
2959  jPoint++;
2960  }
2961  }
2962 
2963  /*--- Gather the data on the master node. ---*/
2964 
2965 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
2966  SU2_MPI::Gather(Buffer_Send_Var, nBuffer_Scalar, MPI_DOUBLE, Buffer_Recv_Var, nBuffer_Scalar, MPI_DOUBLE, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
2967  if (!config->GetDiscrete_Adjoint())
2968  SU2_MPI::Gather(Buffer_Send_Res, nBuffer_Scalar, MPI_DOUBLE, Buffer_Recv_Res, nBuffer_Scalar, MPI_DOUBLE, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
2969 #else
2970  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nBuffer_Scalar; iPoint++) Buffer_Recv_Var[iPoint] = Buffer_Send_Var[iPoint];
2971  if (!config->GetDiscrete_Adjoint())
2972  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nBuffer_Scalar; iPoint++) Buffer_Recv_Res[iPoint] = Buffer_Send_Res[iPoint];
2973 #endif
2974 
2975  /*--- The master node unpacks and sorts this variable by global index ---*/
2976 
2977  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) {
2978  jPoint = 0; iVar = iVar_Sens;
2979  for (iProcessor = 0; iProcessor < size; iProcessor++) {
2980  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < Buffer_Recv_nPoint[iProcessor]; iPoint++) {
2981

2983

2985  Data[iVar+0][iGlobal_Index] = Buffer_Recv_Var[jPoint];
2986  if (!config->GetDiscrete_Adjoint())
2987  Data[iVar+1][iGlobal_Index] = Buffer_Recv_Res[jPoint];

2989  }
2990

3444 
3445 void COutput::MergeBaselineSolution(CConfig *config, CGeometry *geometry, CSolver *solver, unsigned short val_iZone) {
3446 
3447  /*--- Local variables needed on all processors ---*/
3448  unsigned short iVar;
3449  unsigned long iPoint = 0, jPoint = 0;
3450 
3451  nVar_Total = config->fields.size() - 1;
3452 
3453  /*--- Merge the solution either in serial or parallel. ---*/
3454 
3455 #ifndef HAVE_MPI
3456 
3457  /*--- In serial, the single process has access to all solution data,
3458  so it is simple to retrieve and store inside Solution_Data. ---*/
3459 
3460  unsigned short iMarker;
3461  unsigned long iVertex, nTotalPoints = 0;
3462  int SendRecv;
3463 
3464  /*--- First, create a structure to locate any periodic halo nodes ---*/
3465  int *Local_Halo = new int[geometry->GetnPoint()];
3466  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < geometry->GetnPoint(); iPoint++)
3467  Local_Halo[iPoint] = !geometry->node[iPoint]->GetDomain();
3468 
3469  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
3470  if (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == SEND_RECEIVE) {
3471  SendRecv = config->GetMarker_All_SendRecv(iMarker);
3472  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
3473  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
3474  if ((geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetRotation_Type() > 0) &&
3475  (geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetRotation_Type() % 2 == 1) &&
3476  (SendRecv < 0)) {
3477  Local_Halo[iPoint] = false;
3478  }
3479  }
3480 
3481  }
3482  }
3483 
3484  /*--- Total number of points in the mesh (this might include periodic points). ---*/
3485 
3486  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < geometry->GetnPoint(); iPoint++)
3487  if (!Local_Halo[iPoint]) nTotalPoints++;
3488 
3489  nGlobal_Poin = nTotalPoints;
3490  Data = new su2double*[nVar_Total];
3491  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar_Total; iVar++) {
3492  Data[iVar] = new su2double[nGlobal_Poin];
3493  }
3494 
3495  /*--- Loop over all points in the mesh, but only write data
3496  for nodes in the domain (ignore periodic halo nodes). ---*/
3497 
3498  jPoint = 0;
3499  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < geometry->GetnPoint(); iPoint++) {
3500  if (!Local_Halo[iPoint]) {
3501 
3502  /*--- Solution (first, and second system of equations) ---*/
3503 
3504  unsigned short jVar = 0;
3505  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar_Total; iVar++) {
3506  Data[jVar][jPoint] = solver->node[iPoint]->GetSolution(iVar);
3507  jVar++;
3508  }
3509  }
3510 
3511  /*--- Increment jPoint as the counter. We need this because iPoint
3512  may include halo nodes that we skip over during this loop. ---*/
3513 
3514  jPoint++;
3515 
3516  }
3517 
3518 #else
3519 
3520  /*--- MPI preprocessing ---*/
3521 
3522  int rank, nProcessor, iProcessor;
3523  MPI_Comm_rank(MPI_COMM_WORLD, &rank);
3524  MPI_Comm_size(MPI_COMM_WORLD, &nProcessor);
3525 
3526  /*--- Local variables needed for merging with MPI ---*/
3527 
3528  unsigned long iVertex, iMarker;
3529  unsigned long Buffer_Send_nPoint[1], *Buffer_Recv_nPoint = NULL;
3530  unsigned long nLocalPoint = 0, MaxLocalPoint = 0;
3531  unsigned long iGlobal_Index = 0, nBuffer_Scalar = 0;
3532 
3533  int *Local_Halo = new int[geometry->GetnPoint()];
3534  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < geometry->GetnPoint(); iPoint++)
3535  Local_Halo[iPoint] = !geometry->node[iPoint]->GetDomain();
3536 
3537  bool Wrt_Halo = config->GetWrt_Halo(), isPeriodic;
3538 
3539  /*--- Search all send/recv boundaries on this partition for any periodic
3540  nodes that were part of the original domain. We want to recover these
3541  for visualization purposes. ---*/
3542 
3543  if (Wrt_Halo) {
3544  nLocalPoint = geometry->GetnPoint();
3545  } else {
3546  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
3547  if (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == SEND_RECEIVE) {
3548 
3549  /*--- Checking for less than or equal to the rank, because there may
3550  be some periodic halo nodes that send info to the same rank. ---*/
3551 
3552  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
3553  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
3554  isPeriodic = ((geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetRotation_Type() > 0) &&
3555  (geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetRotation_Type() % 2 == 1));
3556  if (isPeriodic) Local_Halo[iPoint] = false;
3557  }
3558  }
3559  }
3560 
3561  /*--- Sum total number of nodes that belong to the domain ---*/
3562 
3563  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < geometry->GetnPoint(); iPoint++)
3564  if (Local_Halo[iPoint] == false)
3565  nLocalPoint++;
3566 
3567  }
3568  Buffer_Send_nPoint[0] = nLocalPoint;
3569 
3570  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) Buffer_Recv_nPoint = new unsigned long[nProcessor];
3571 
3572  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&nLocalPoint, &MaxLocalPoint, 1, MPI_UNSIGNED_LONG, MPI_MAX, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
3573  SU2_MPI::Gather(&Buffer_Send_nPoint, 1, MPI_UNSIGNED_LONG, Buffer_Recv_nPoint, 1, MPI_UNSIGNED_LONG, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
3574 
3575  nBuffer_Scalar = MaxLocalPoint;
3576 
3577  /*--- Send and Recv buffers. ---*/
3578 
3579  su2double *Buffer_Send_Var = new su2double[MaxLocalPoint];
3580  su2double *Buffer_Recv_Var = NULL;
3581 
3582  unsigned long *Buffer_Send_GlobalIndex = new unsigned long[MaxLocalPoint];
3583  unsigned long *Buffer_Recv_GlobalIndex = NULL;
3584 
3585  /*--- Prepare the receive buffers in the master node only. ---*/
3586  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) {
3587 
3588  Buffer_Recv_Var = new su2double[nProcessor*MaxLocalPoint];
3589  Buffer_Recv_GlobalIndex = new unsigned long[nProcessor*MaxLocalPoint];
3590 
3591  /*--- Sum total number of nodes to be written and allocate arrays ---*/
3592  nGlobal_Poin = 0;
3593  for (iProcessor = 0; iProcessor < nProcessor; iProcessor++) {
3594  nGlobal_Poin += Buffer_Recv_nPoint[iProcessor];
3595  }
3596  Data = new su2double*[nVar_Total];
3597  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar_Total; iVar++) {
3598  Data[iVar] = new su2double[nGlobal_Poin];
3599  }
3600 
3601  }
3602 
3603  /*--- Main communication routine. Loop over each variable that has
3604  been requested by the user and perform the MPI comm. Temporary
3605  1-D buffers are used to send the solution for each variable at all
3606  nodes on each partition to the master node. These are then unpacked
3607  by the master and sorted by global index in one large n-dim. array. ---*/
3608 
3609  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar_Total; iVar++) {
3610 
3611  /*--- Loop over this partition to collect the current variable ---*/
3612  jPoint = 0;
3613  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < geometry->GetnPoint(); iPoint++) {
3614 
3615  /*--- Check for halos and write only if requested ---*/
3616  if (!Local_Halo[iPoint] || Wrt_Halo) {
3617 
3618  /*--- Get this variable into the temporary send buffer. ---*/
3619  Buffer_Send_Var[jPoint] = solver->node[iPoint]->GetSolution(iVar);
3620 
3621  /*--- Only send/recv the volumes & global indices during the first loop ---*/
3622  if (iVar == 0) {
3623  Buffer_Send_GlobalIndex[jPoint] = geometry->node[iPoint]->GetGlobalIndex();
3624  }
3625  jPoint++;
3626  }
3627  }
3628 
3629  /*--- Gather the data on the master node. ---*/
3630 
3631  SU2_MPI::Gather(Buffer_Send_Var, nBuffer_Scalar, MPI_DOUBLE, Buffer_Recv_Var, nBuffer_Scalar, MPI_DOUBLE, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
3632  if (iVar == 0) {
3633  SU2_MPI::Gather(Buffer_Send_GlobalIndex, nBuffer_Scalar, MPI_UNSIGNED_LONG, Buffer_Recv_GlobalIndex, nBuffer_Scalar, MPI_UNSIGNED_LONG, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
3634  }
3635 
3636  /*--- The master node unpacks and sorts this variable by global index ---*/
3637  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) {
3638  jPoint = 0;
3639  for (iProcessor = 0; iProcessor < nProcessor; iProcessor++) {
3640  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < Buffer_Recv_nPoint[iProcessor]; iPoint++) {
3641 
3642  /*--- Get global index, then loop over each variable and store ---*/
3643  iGlobal_Index = Buffer_Recv_GlobalIndex[jPoint];
3644  Data[iVar][iGlobal_Index] = Buffer_Recv_Var[jPoint];
3645  jPoint++;
3646  }
3647  /*--- Adjust jPoint to index of next proc's data in the buffers. ---*/
3648  jPoint = (iProcessor+1)*nBuffer_Scalar;
3649  }
3650  }
3651  }
3652 
3653  /*--- Immediately release the temporary buffers. ---*/
3654 
3655  delete [] Buffer_Send_Var;
3656  delete [] Buffer_Send_GlobalIndex;
3657  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) {
3658  delete [] Buffer_Recv_Var;
3659  delete [] Buffer_Recv_GlobalIndex;
3660  }
3661 
3662 #endif
3663 
3664  delete [] Local_Halo;
3665 
3666 }
3667 
3668 void COutput::SetRestart(CConfig *config, CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver, unsigned short val_iZone) {
3669 
3670  /*--- Local variables ---*/
3671 
3672  unsigned short nZone = geometry->GetnZone();
3673  unsigned short Kind_Solver = config->GetKind_Solver();
3674  unsigned short iVar, iDim, nDim = geometry->GetnDim();
3675  unsigned long iPoint, iExtIter = config->GetExtIter();
3676  bool grid_movement = config->GetGrid_Movement();
3677  bool dynamic_fem = (config->GetDynamic_Analysis() == DYNAMIC);
3678  bool fem = (config->GetKind_Solver() == FEM_ELASTICITY);
3679  ofstream restart_file;
3680  string filename;
3681 
3682  /*--- Retrieve filename from config ---*/
3683 
3684  if ((config->GetContinuous_Adjoint()) || (config->GetDiscrete_Adjoint())) {
3685  filename = config->GetRestart_AdjFileName();
3686  filename = config->GetObjFunc_Extension(filename);
3687  } else if (fem){
3688  filename = config->GetRestart_FEMFileName();
3689  } else {
3690  filename = config->GetRestart_FlowFileName();
3691  }
3692 
3693  /*--- Append the zone number if multizone problems ---*/
3694  if (nZone > 1)
3695  filename= config->GetMultizone_FileName(filename, val_iZone);
3696 
3697  /*--- Unsteady problems require an iteration number to be appended. ---*/
3698  if (config->GetUnsteady_Simulation() == TIME_SPECTRAL) {
3699  filename = config->GetUnsteady_FileName(filename, SU2_TYPE::Int(val_iZone));
3700  } else if (config->GetWrt_Unsteady()) {
3701  filename = config->GetUnsteady_FileName(filename, SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter));
3702  } else if ((fem) && (config->GetWrt_Dynamic())) {
3703  filename = config->GetUnsteady_FileName(filename, SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter));
3704  }
3705 
3706  /*--- Open the restart file and write the solution. ---*/
3707 
3708  restart_file.open(filename.c_str(), ios::out);
3709  restart_file.precision(15);
3710 
3711  /*--- Write the header line based on the particular solver ----*/
3712 
3713  restart_file << "\"PointID\"";
3714 
3715  /*--- Mesh coordinates are always written to the restart first ---*/
3716 
3717  if (nDim == 2) {
3718  restart_file << "\t\"x\"\t\"y\"";
3719  } else {
3720  restart_file << "\t\"x\"\t\"y\"\t\"z\"";
3721  }
3722 
3723  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar_Consv; iVar++) {
3724  if ( Kind_Solver == FEM_ELASTICITY )
3725  restart_file << "\t\"Displacement_" << iVar+1<<"\"";
3726  else
3727  restart_file << "\t\"Conservative_" << iVar+1<<"\"";
3728  }
3729 
3730  if (!config->GetLow_MemoryOutput()) {
3731 
3732  if (config->GetWrt_Limiters()) {
3733  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar_Consv; iVar++) {
3734  restart_file << "\t\"Limiter_" << iVar+1<<"\"";
3735  }
3736  }
3737  if (config->GetWrt_Residuals()) {
3738  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar_Consv; iVar++) {
3739  restart_file << "\t\"Residual_" << iVar+1<<"\"";
3740  }
3741  }
3742 
3743  /*--- Mesh velocities for dynamic mesh cases ---*/
3744 
3745  if (grid_movement && !fem) {
3746  if (nDim == 2) {
3747  restart_file << "\t\"Grid_Velx\"\t\"Grid_Vely\"";
3748  } else {
3749  restart_file << "\t\"Grid_Velx\"\t\"Grid_Vely\"\t\"Grid_Velz\"";
3750  }
3751  }
3752 
3753  /*--- Solver specific output variables ---*/
3754 
3755  if (config->GetKind_Regime() == FREESURFACE) {
3756  restart_file << "\t\"Density\"";
3757  }
3758 
3759  if ((Kind_Solver == EULER) || (Kind_Solver == NAVIER_STOKES) || (Kind_Solver == RANS)) {
3760  if (config->GetOutput_FileFormat() == PARAVIEW) {
3761  restart_file << "\t\"Pressure\"\t\"Temperature\"\t\"Pressure_Coefficient\"\t\"Mach\"";
3762  } else
3763  restart_file << "\t\"Pressure\"\t\"Temperature\"\t\"C<sub>p</sub>\"\t\"Mach\"";
3764  }
3765 
3766  if ((Kind_Solver == NAVIER_STOKES) || (Kind_Solver == RANS)) {
3767  if (config->GetOutput_FileFormat() == PARAVIEW) {
3768  if (nDim == 2) restart_file << "\t\"Laminar_Viscosity\"\t\"Skin_Friction_Coefficient_X\"\t\"Skin_Friction_Coefficient_Y\"\t\"Heat_Flux\"\t\"Y_Plus\"";
3769  if (nDim == 3) restart_file << "\t\"Laminar_Viscosity\"\t\"Skin_Friction_Coefficient_X\"\t\"Skin_Friction_Coefficient_Y\"\t\"Skin_Friction_Coefficient_Z\"\t\"Heat_Flux\"\t\"Y_Plus\"";
3770  } else {
3771  if (nDim == 2) restart_file << "\t\"<greek>m</greek>\"\t\"C<sub>f</sub>_x\"\t\"C<sub>f</sub>_y\"\t\"h\"\t\"y<sup>+</sup>\"";
3772  if (nDim == 3) restart_file << "\t\"<greek>m</greek>\"\t\"C<sub>f</sub>_x\"\t\"C<sub>f</sub>_y\"\t\"C<sub>f</sub>_z\"\t\"h\"\t\"y<sup>+</sup>\"";
3773  }
3774  }
3775 
3776  if (Kind_Solver == RANS) {
3777  if (config->GetOutput_FileFormat() == PARAVIEW) {
3778  restart_file << "\t\"Eddy_Viscosity\"";
3779  } else
3780  restart_file << "\t\"<greek>m</greek><sub>t</sub>\"";
3781  }
3782 
3783  if (config->GetWrt_SharpEdges()) {
3784  if ((Kind_Solver == EULER) || (Kind_Solver == NAVIER_STOKES) || (Kind_Solver == RANS)) {
3785  restart_file << "\t\"Sharp_Edge_Dist\"";
3786  }
3787  }
3788 
3789  if (Kind_Solver == POISSON_EQUATION) {
3790  for (iDim = 0; iDim < geometry->GetnDim(); iDim++)
3791  restart_file << "\t\"poissonField_" << iDim+1 << "\"";
3792  }
3793 
3794  if ((Kind_Solver == ADJ_EULER ) ||
3795  (Kind_Solver == ADJ_NAVIER_STOKES ) ||
3796  (Kind_Solver == ADJ_RANS ) ) {
3797  restart_file << "\t\"Surface_Sensitivity\"\t\"Solution_Sensor\"";
3798  }
3799  if (( Kind_Solver == DISC_ADJ_EULER ) ||
3800  ( Kind_Solver == DISC_ADJ_NAVIER_STOKES ) ||
3801  ( Kind_Solver == DISC_ADJ_RANS )) {
3802  restart_file << "\t\"Surface_Sensitivity\"\t\"Sensitivity_x\"\t\"Sensitivity_y\"";
3803  if (geometry->GetnDim() == 3){
3804  restart_file << "\t\"Sensitivity_z\"";
3805  }
3806  }
3807 
3808  if (Kind_Solver == FEM_ELASTICITY) {
3809  if (!dynamic_fem) {
3810  if (geometry->GetnDim() == 2)
3811  restart_file << "\t\"Sxx\"\t\"Syy\"\t\"Sxy\"\t\"Von_Mises_Stress\"";
3812  if (geometry->GetnDim() == 3)
3813  restart_file << "\t\"Sxx\"\t\"Syy\"\t\"Sxy\"\t\"Szz\"\t\"Sxz\"\t\"Syz\"\t\"Von_Mises_Stress\"";
3814  }
3815  else if (dynamic_fem) {
3816  if (geometry->GetnDim() == 2){
3817  restart_file << "\t\"Velocity_1\"\t\"Velocity_2\"\t\"Acceleration_1\"\t\"Acceleration_2\"";
3818  restart_file << "\t\"Sxx\"\t\"Syy\"\t\"Sxy\"\t\"Von_Mises_Stress\"";
3819  }
3820  if (geometry->GetnDim() == 3){
3821  restart_file << "\t\"Velocity_1\"\t\"Velocity_2\"\t\"Velocity_3\"\t\"Acceleration_1\"\t\"Acceleration_2\"\t\"Acceleration_3\"";
3822  restart_file << "\t\"Sxx\"\t\"Syy\"\t\"Sxy\"\t\"Szz\"\t\"Sxz\"\t\"Syz\"\t\"Von_Mises_Stress\"";
3823  }
3824  }
3825  }
3826 
3827 
3828  if (config->GetExtraOutput()) {
3829  string *headings = NULL;
3830  //if (Kind_Solver == RANS) {
3831  headings = solver[TURB_SOL]->OutputHeadingNames;
3832  //}
3833 
3834  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar_Extra; iVar++) {
3835  if (headings == NULL) {
3836  restart_file << "\t\"ExtraOutput_" << iVar+1<<"\"";
3837  } else{
3838  restart_file << "\t\""<< headings[iVar] <<"\"";
3839  }
3840  }
3841  }
3842  }
3843 
3844  restart_file << "\n";
3845 
3846  /*--- Write the restart file ---*/
3847 
3848  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < geometry->GetGlobal_nPointDomain(); iPoint++) {
3849 
3850  /*--- Index of the point ---*/
3851  restart_file << iPoint << "\t";
3852 
3853  /*--- Write the grid coordinates first ---*/
3854  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
3855  restart_file << scientific << Coords[iDim][iPoint] << "\t";
3856  }
3857 
3858  /*--- Loop over the variables and write the values to file ---*/
3859  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar_Total; iVar++) {
3860  restart_file << scientific << Data[iVar][iPoint] << "\t";
3861  }
3862  restart_file << "\n";
3863  }
3864 
3865  restart_file.close();
3866 
3867 }

3869 void COutput::DeallocateCoordinates(CConfig *config, CGeometry *geometry) {

3872

3876 #endif
3877 
3878  /*--- The master node alone owns all data found in this routine. ---*/
3879 
3880  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) {
3881

3883

3938 void COutput::SetConvHistory_Header(ofstream *ConvHist_file, CConfig *config) {
3939  char cstr[200], buffer[50], turb_resid[1000];
3940  unsigned short iMarker, iMarker_Monitoring;
3941  string Monitoring_Tag, monitoring_coeff, aeroelastic_coeff;
3942 
3943  bool rotating_frame = config->GetRotating_Frame();
3944  bool aeroelastic = config->GetAeroelastic_Simulation();
3945  bool equiv_area = config->GetEquivArea();
3946  bool turbulent = ((config->GetKind_Solver() == RANS) || (config->GetKind_Solver() == ADJ_RANS) ||
3947  (config->GetKind_Solver() == DISC_ADJ_RANS));
3948  bool frozen_turb = config->GetFrozen_Visc();
3949  bool freesurface = (config->GetKind_Regime() == FREESURFACE);
3950  bool inv_design = (config->GetInvDesign_Cp() || config->GetInvDesign_HeatFlux());
3951  bool output_1d = config->GetWrt_1D_Output();
3952  bool output_per_surface = false;
3953  bool output_massflow = (config->GetKind_ObjFunc() == MASS_FLOW_RATE);
3954  if (config->GetnMarker_Monitoring() > 1) output_per_surface = true;
3955 
3956  unsigned short direct_diff = config->GetDirectDiff();
3957 
3958  bool isothermal = false;
3959  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++)
3960  if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ISOTHERMAL ))
3961  isothermal = true;
3962 
3963  /*--- Write file name with extension ---*/
3964 
3965  string filename = config->GetConv_FileName();
3966  strcpy (cstr, filename.data());
3967 
3968  if (config->GetWrt_Unsteady() && config->GetRestart()) {
3969  long iExtIter = config->GetUnst_RestartIter();
3970  if (SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter) < 10) SPRINTF (buffer, "_0000%d", SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter));
3971  if ((SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter) >= 10) && (SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter) < 100)) SPRINTF (buffer, "_000%d", SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter));
3972  if ((SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter) >= 100) && (SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter) < 1000)) SPRINTF (buffer, "_00%d", SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter));
3973  if ((SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter) >= 1000) && (SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter) < 10000)) SPRINTF (buffer, "_0%d", SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter));
3974  if (SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter) >= 10000) SPRINTF (buffer, "_%d", SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter));
3975  strcat(cstr, buffer);
3976  }
3977 
3978  if ((config->GetOutput_FileFormat() == TECPLOT) ||
3979  (config->GetOutput_FileFormat() == FIELDVIEW)) SPRINTF (buffer, ".dat");
3980  else if ((config->GetOutput_FileFormat() == TECPLOT_BINARY) ||
3981  (config->GetOutput_FileFormat() == FIELDVIEW_BINARY)) SPRINTF (buffer, ".plt");
3982  else if (config->GetOutput_FileFormat() == PARAVIEW) SPRINTF (buffer, ".csv");
3983  strcat(cstr, buffer);
3984 
3985  ConvHist_file->open(cstr, ios::out);
3986  ConvHist_file->precision(15);
3987 
3988  /*--- Begin of the header ---*/
3989 
3990  char begin[]= "\"Iteration\"";
3991 
3992  /*--- Header for the coefficients ---*/
3993 
3994  char flow_coeff[]= ",\"CLift\",\"CDrag\",\"CSideForce\",\"CMx\",\"CMy\",\"CMz\",\"CFx\",\"CFy\",\"CFz\",\"CL/CD\"";
3995  char heat_coeff[]= ",\"HeatFlux_Total\",\"HeatFlux_Maximum\"";
3996  char equivalent_area_coeff[]= ",\"CEquivArea\",\"CNearFieldOF\"";
3997  char rotating_frame_coeff[]= ",\"CMerit\",\"CT\",\"CQ\"";
3998  char free_surface_coeff[]= ",\"CFreeSurface\"";
3999  char wave_coeff[]= ",\"CWave\"";
4000  char fem_coeff[]= ",\"VM_Stress\"";
4001  char adj_coeff[]= ",\"Sens_Geo\",\"Sens_Mach\",\"Sens_AoA\",\"Sens_Press\",\"Sens_Temp\",\"Sens_AoS\"";
4002  char oneD_outputs[]= ",\"Avg_TotalPress\",\"Avg_Mach\",\"Avg_Temperature\",\"MassFlowRate\",\"FluxAvg_Pressure\",\"FluxAvg_Density\",\"FluxAvg_Velocity\",\"FluxAvg_Enthalpy\"";
4003  char Cp_inverse_design[]= ",\"Cp_Diff\"";
4004  char Heat_inverse_design[]= ",\"HeatFlux_Diff\"";
4005  char mass_flow_rate[] = ",\"MassFlowRate\"";
4006  char d_flow_coeff[] = ",\"D(CLift)\",\"D(CDrag)\",\"D(CSideForce)\",\"D(CMx)\",\"D(CMy)\",\"D(CMz)\",\"D(CFx)\",\"D(CFy)\",\"D(CFz)\",\"D(CL/CD)\"";
4007 
4008  /* Find the markers being monitored and create a header for them */
4009  for (iMarker_Monitoring = 0; iMarker_Monitoring < config->GetnMarker_Monitoring(); iMarker_Monitoring++) {
4010  Monitoring_Tag = config->GetMarker_Monitoring(iMarker_Monitoring);
4011  monitoring_coeff += ",\"CLift_" + Monitoring_Tag + "\"";
4012  monitoring_coeff += ",\"CDrag_" + Monitoring_Tag + "\"";
4013  monitoring_coeff += ",\"CSideForce_" + Monitoring_Tag + "\"";
4014  monitoring_coeff += ",\"CL/CD_" + Monitoring_Tag + "\"";
4015  monitoring_coeff += ",\"CFx_" + Monitoring_Tag + "\"";
4016  monitoring_coeff += ",\"CFy_" + Monitoring_Tag + "\"";
4017  monitoring_coeff += ",\"CFz_" + Monitoring_Tag + "\"";
4018  monitoring_coeff += ",\"CMx_" + Monitoring_Tag + "\"";
4019  monitoring_coeff += ",\"CMy_" + Monitoring_Tag + "\"";
4020  monitoring_coeff += ",\"CMz_" + Monitoring_Tag + "\"";
4021  aeroelastic_coeff += ",\"plunge_" + Monitoring_Tag + "\"";
4022  aeroelastic_coeff += ",\"pitch_" + Monitoring_Tag + "\"";
4023  }
4024 
4025  /*--- Header for the residuals ---*/
4026 
4027  char flow_resid[]= ",\"Res_Flow[0]\",\"Res_Flow[1]\",\"Res_Flow[2]\",\"Res_Flow[3]\",\"Res_Flow[4]\"";
4028  char adj_flow_resid[]= ",\"Res_AdjFlow[0]\",\"Res_AdjFlow[1]\",\"Res_AdjFlow[2]\",\"Res_AdjFlow[3]\",\"Res_AdjFlow[4]\"";
4029  switch (config->GetKind_Turb_Model()) {
4030  case SA: SPRINTF (turb_resid, ",\"Res_Turb[0]\""); break;
4031  case SA_NEG: SPRINTF (turb_resid, ",\"Res_Turb[0]\""); break;
4032  case SST: SPRINTF (turb_resid, ",\"Res_Turb[0]\",\"Res_Turb[1]\""); break;
4033  }
4034  char adj_turb_resid[]= ",\"Res_AdjTurb[0]\"";
4035  char levelset_resid[]= ",\"Res_LevelSet\"";
4036  char adj_levelset_resid[]= ",\"Res_AdjLevelSet\"";
4037  char wave_resid[]= ",\"Res_Wave[0]\",\"Res_Wave[1]\"";
4038  char fem_resid[]= ",\"Res_FEM[0]\",\"Res_FEM[1]\",\"Res_FEM[2]\"";
4039  char heat_resid[]= ",\"Res_Heat\"";
4040 
4041  /*--- End of the header ---*/
4042 
4043  char end[]= ",\"Linear_Solver_Iterations\",\"CFL_Number\",\"Time(min)\"\n";
4044 
4045  if ((config->GetOutput_FileFormat() == TECPLOT) ||
4046  (config->GetOutput_FileFormat() == TECPLOT_BINARY) ||
4047  (config->GetOutput_FileFormat() == FIELDVIEW) ||
4048  (config->GetOutput_FileFormat() == FIELDVIEW_BINARY)) {
4049  ConvHist_file[0] << "TITLE = \"SU2 Simulation\"" << endl;
4050  ConvHist_file[0] << "VARIABLES = ";
4051  }
4052 
4053  /*--- Write the header, case depending ---*/
4054  switch (config->GetKind_Solver()) {
4055 
4056  case EULER : case NAVIER_STOKES: case RANS :
4057  ConvHist_file[0] << begin << flow_coeff;
4058  if (isothermal) ConvHist_file[0] << heat_coeff;
4059  if (equiv_area) ConvHist_file[0] << equivalent_area_coeff;
4060  if (inv_design) {
4061  ConvHist_file[0] << Cp_inverse_design;
4062  if (isothermal) ConvHist_file[0] << Heat_inverse_design;
4063  }
4064  if (rotating_frame) ConvHist_file[0] << rotating_frame_coeff;
4065  ConvHist_file[0] << flow_resid;
4066  if (turbulent) ConvHist_file[0] << turb_resid;
4067  if (aeroelastic) ConvHist_file[0] << aeroelastic_coeff;
4068  if (output_per_surface) ConvHist_file[0] << monitoring_coeff;
4069  if (output_1d) ConvHist_file[0] << oneD_outputs;
4070  if (output_massflow && !output_1d) ConvHist_file[0]<< mass_flow_rate;
4071  if (direct_diff != NO_DERIVATIVE) ConvHist_file[0] << d_flow_coeff;
4072  ConvHist_file[0] << end;
4073  if (freesurface) {
4074  ConvHist_file[0] << begin << flow_coeff << free_surface_coeff;
4075  ConvHist_file[0] << flow_resid << levelset_resid << end;
4076  }
4077 
4078  break;
4079 
4080  case ADJ_EULER : case ADJ_NAVIER_STOKES : case ADJ_RANS:
4081  case DISC_ADJ_EULER: case DISC_ADJ_NAVIER_STOKES: case DISC_ADJ_RANS:
4082  ConvHist_file[0] << begin << adj_coeff << adj_flow_resid;
4083  if ((turbulent) && (!frozen_turb)) ConvHist_file[0] << adj_turb_resid;
4084  ConvHist_file[0] << end;
4085  if (freesurface) {
4086  ConvHist_file[0] << begin << adj_coeff << adj_flow_resid << adj_levelset_resid << end;
4087  }
4088  break;
4089 
4090  case WAVE_EQUATION:
4091  ConvHist_file[0] << begin << wave_coeff;
4092  ConvHist_file[0] << wave_resid << end;
4093  break;
4094 
4095  case HEAT_EQUATION:
4096  ConvHist_file[0] << begin << heat_coeff;
4097  ConvHist_file[0] << heat_resid << end;
4098  break;
4099 
4100  case FEM_ELASTICITY:
4101  ConvHist_file[0] << begin << fem_coeff;
4102  ConvHist_file[0] << fem_resid << end;
4103  break;
4104 
4105  }
4106 
4107  if (config->GetOutput_FileFormat() == TECPLOT ||
4108  config->GetOutput_FileFormat() == TECPLOT_BINARY ||
4109  config->GetOutput_FileFormat() == FIELDVIEW ||
4110  config->GetOutput_FileFormat() == FIELDVIEW_BINARY) {
4111  ConvHist_file[0] << "ZONE T= \"Convergence history\"" << endl;
4112  }
4113 
4114 }

4116 
4117 void COutput::SetConvHistory_Body(ofstream *ConvHist_file,
4118  CGeometry ***geometry,
4119  CSolver ****solver_container,
4120  CConfig **config,
4121  CIntegration ***integration,
4122  bool DualTime_Iteration,
4123  su2double timeused,
4124  unsigned short val_iZone) {
4125 
4126  bool output_1d = config[val_iZone]->GetWrt_1D_Output();
4127  bool output_massflow = (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_ObjFunc() == MASS_FLOW_RATE);
4128  unsigned short FinestMesh = config[val_iZone]->GetFinestMesh();
4129 
4130  int rank;
4131 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
4132  MPI_Comm_rank(MPI_COMM_WORLD, &rank);
4133 #else
4134  rank = MASTER_NODE;
4135 #endif
4136 
4137  /*--- If 1-D outputs requested, calculated them. Requires info from all nodes,
4138  Get area-averaged and flux-averaged values at the specified surface ---*/
4139 
4140  if (output_1d) {
4141  switch (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver()) {
4142  case EULER: case NAVIER_STOKES: case RANS:
4143  case ADJ_EULER: case ADJ_NAVIER_STOKES: case ADJ_RANS:
4144  OneDimensionalOutput(solver_container[val_iZone][FinestMesh][FLOW_SOL], geometry[val_iZone][FinestMesh], config[val_iZone]);
4145  break;
4146  }
4147  }
4148  if (output_massflow && !output_1d) {
4149  switch (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver()) {
4150  case EULER: case NAVIER_STOKES: case RANS:
4151  case ADJ_EULER: case ADJ_NAVIER_STOKES: case ADJ_RANS:
4152  SetMassFlowRate(solver_container[val_iZone][FinestMesh][FLOW_SOL], geometry[val_iZone][FinestMesh], config[val_iZone]);
4153  break;
4154  }
4155  }
4156 
4157  /*--- Output using only the master node ---*/
4158  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) {
4159 
4160  unsigned long iIntIter = config[val_iZone]->GetIntIter();
4161  unsigned long iExtIter = config[val_iZone]->GetExtIter();
4162 
4163  /*--- WARNING: These buffers have hard-coded lengths. Note that you
4164  may have to adjust them to be larger if adding more entries. ---*/
4165  char begin[1000], direct_coeff[1000], surface_coeff[1000], aeroelastic_coeff[1000], monitoring_coeff[10000],
4166  adjoint_coeff[1000], flow_resid[1000], adj_flow_resid[1000], turb_resid[1000], trans_resid[1000],
4167  adj_turb_resid[1000], levelset_resid[1000], adj_levelset_resid[1000], wave_coeff[1000],
4168  heat_coeff[1000], fem_coeff[1000], wave_resid[1000], heat_resid[1000],
4169  fem_resid[1000], end[1000], oneD_outputs[1000], massflow_outputs[1000], d_direct_coeff[1000];
4170 
4171  su2double dummy = 0.0, *Coord;
4172  unsigned short iVar, iMarker, iMarker_Monitoring;
4173 
4174  unsigned long LinSolvIter = 0, iPointMaxResid;
4175  su2double timeiter = timeused/su2double(iExtIter+1);
4176 
4177  unsigned short nDim = geometry[val_iZone][FinestMesh]->GetnDim();
4178 
4179  bool compressible = (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Regime() == COMPRESSIBLE);
4180  bool incompressible = (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Regime() == INCOMPRESSIBLE);
4181  bool freesurface = (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Regime() == FREESURFACE);
4182 
4183  bool rotating_frame = config[val_iZone]->GetRotating_Frame();
4184  bool aeroelastic = config[val_iZone]->GetAeroelastic_Simulation();
4185  bool equiv_area = config[val_iZone]->GetEquivArea();
4186  bool inv_design = (config[val_iZone]->GetInvDesign_Cp() || config[val_iZone]->GetInvDesign_HeatFlux());
4187  bool transition = (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Trans_Model() == LM);
4188  bool isothermal = false;
4189  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config[val_iZone]->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++)
4190  if ((config[val_iZone]->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ISOTHERMAL))
4191  isothermal = true;
4192  bool turbulent = ((config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == RANS) || (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == ADJ_RANS) ||
4193  (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == DISC_ADJ_RANS));
4194  bool adjoint = config[val_iZone]->GetContinuous_Adjoint() || config[val_iZone]->GetDiscrete_Adjoint();
4195  bool disc_adj = config[val_iZone]->GetDiscrete_Adjoint();
4196  bool wave = (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == WAVE_EQUATION);
4197  bool heat = (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == HEAT_EQUATION);
4198  bool flow = (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == EULER) || (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == NAVIER_STOKES) ||
4199  (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == RANS) || (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == ADJ_EULER) ||
4200  (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == ADJ_NAVIER_STOKES) || (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == ADJ_RANS);
4201 
4202  bool fem = (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == FEM_ELASTICITY); // FEM structural solver.
4203  bool linear_analysis = (config[val_iZone]->GetGeometricConditions() == SMALL_DEFORMATIONS); // Linear analysis.
4204  bool nonlinear_analysis = (config[val_iZone]->GetGeometricConditions() == LARGE_DEFORMATIONS); // Nonlinear analysis.
4205 
4206  bool fsi = (config[val_iZone]->GetFSI_Simulation()); // FEM structural solver.
4207 
4208  bool turbo = config[val_iZone]->GetBoolTurboPerf();
4209  string inMarker_Tag, outMarker_Tag;
4210 
4211  bool output_per_surface = false;
4212  if (config[val_iZone]->GetnMarker_Monitoring() > 1) output_per_surface = true;
4213 
4214  unsigned short direct_diff = config[val_iZone]->GetDirectDiff();
4215 
4216 
4217  /*--- Initialize variables to store information from all domains (direct solution) ---*/
4218  su2double Total_CLift = 0.0, Total_CDrag = 0.0, Total_CSideForce = 0.0, Total_CMx = 0.0, Total_CMy = 0.0, Total_CMz = 0.0, Total_CEff = 0.0,
4219  Total_CEquivArea = 0.0, Total_CNearFieldOF = 0.0, Total_CFx = 0.0, Total_CFy = 0.0, Total_CFz = 0.0, Total_CMerit = 0.0,
4220  Total_CT = 0.0, Total_CQ = 0.0, Total_CFreeSurface = 0.0, Total_CWave = 0.0, Total_CHeat = 0.0, Total_CpDiff = 0.0, Total_HeatFluxDiff = 0.0,
4221  Total_Heat = 0.0, Total_MaxHeat = 0.0, Total_Mdot = 0.0, Total_CFEM = 0.0;
4222  su2double OneD_AvgStagPress = 0.0, OneD_AvgMach = 0.0, OneD_AvgTemp = 0.0, OneD_MassFlowRate = 0.0,
4223  OneD_FluxAvgPress = 0.0, OneD_FluxAvgDensity = 0.0, OneD_FluxAvgVelocity = 0.0, OneD_FluxAvgEntalpy = 0.0;
4224 
4225  /*--- Initialize variables to store information from all zone for turboperformance (direct solution) ---*/
4226  su2double *TotalStaticEfficiency = NULL,
4227  *TotalTotalEfficiency = NULL,
4228  *KineticEnergyLoss = NULL,
4229  *TotalPressureLoss = NULL,
4230  *MassFlowIn = NULL,
4231  *MassFlowOut = NULL,
4232  *FlowAngleIn = NULL,
4233  *FlowAngleOut = NULL,
4234  *EulerianWork = NULL,
4235  *TotalEnthalpyIn = NULL,
4236  *PressureRatio = NULL,
4237  *PressureOut = NULL,
4238  *EnthalpyOut = NULL,
4239  *MachIn = NULL,
4240  *MachOut = NULL,
4241  *NormalMachIn = NULL,
4242  *NormalMachOut = NULL,
4243  *VelocityOutIs = NULL;
4244 
4245  /*--- Initialize variables to store information from all domains (adjoint solution) ---*/
4246  su2double Total_Sens_Geo = 0.0, Total_Sens_Mach = 0.0, Total_Sens_AoA = 0.0;
4247  su2double Total_Sens_Press = 0.0, Total_Sens_Temp = 0.0;
4248 
4249  /*--- Initialize variables to store information from all domains (direct differentiation) ---*/
4250  su2double D_Total_CLift = 0.0, D_Total_CDrag = 0.0, D_Total_CSideForce = 0.0, D_Total_CMx = 0.0, D_Total_CMy = 0.0, D_Total_CMz = 0.0, D_Total_CEff = 0.0, D_Total_CFx = 0.0, D_Total_CFy = 0.0, D_Total_CFz = 0.0;
4251 
4252  /*--- Residual arrays ---*/
4253  su2double *residual_flow = NULL,
4254  *residual_turbulent = NULL,
4255  *residual_transition = NULL,
4256  *residual_levelset = NULL;
4257  su2double *residual_adjflow = NULL,
4258  *residual_adjturbulent = NULL,
4259  *residual_adjlevelset = NULL;
4260  su2double *residual_wave = NULL;
4261  su2double *residual_fea = NULL;
4262  su2double *residual_fem = NULL;
4263  su2double *residual_heat = NULL;
4264 
4265  /*--- Coefficients Monitored arrays ---*/
4266  su2double *aeroelastic_plunge = NULL,
4267  *aeroelastic_pitch = NULL,
4268  *Surface_CLift = NULL,
4269  *Surface_CDrag = NULL,
4270  *Surface_CSideForce = NULL,
4271  *Surface_CEff = NULL,
4272  *Surface_CFx = NULL,
4273  *Surface_CFy = NULL,
4274  *Surface_CFz = NULL,
4275  *Surface_CMx = NULL,
4276  *Surface_CMy = NULL,
4277  *Surface_CMz = NULL;
4278 
4279  /*--- Initialize number of variables ---*/
4280  unsigned short nVar_Flow = 0, nVar_LevelSet = 0, nVar_Turb = 0,
4281  nVar_Trans = 0, nVar_Wave = 0, nVar_Heat = 0,
4282  nVar_AdjFlow = 0, nVar_AdjLevelSet = 0, nVar_AdjTurb = 0,
4283  nVar_FEM = 0;
4284 
4285  /*--- Direct problem variables ---*/
4286  if (compressible) nVar_Flow = nDim+2; else nVar_Flow = nDim+1;
4287  if (turbulent) {
4288  switch (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Turb_Model()) {
4289  case SA: nVar_Turb = 1; break;
4290  case SA_NEG: nVar_Turb = 1; break;
4291  case SST: nVar_Turb = 2; break;
4292  }
4293  }
4294  if (transition) nVar_Trans = 2;
4295  if (wave) nVar_Wave = 2;
4296  if (heat) nVar_Heat = 1;
4297  if (freesurface) nVar_LevelSet = 1;
4298 
4299  if (fem) {
4300  if (linear_analysis) nVar_FEM = nDim;
4301  if (nonlinear_analysis) nVar_FEM = 3;
4302  }
4303 
4304  /*--- Adjoint problem variables ---*/
4305  if (compressible) nVar_AdjFlow = nDim+2; else nVar_AdjFlow = nDim+1;
4306  if (turbulent) {
4307  switch (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Turb_Model()) {
4308  case SA: nVar_AdjTurb = 1; break;
4309  case SA_NEG: nVar_AdjTurb = 1; break;
4310  case SST: nVar_AdjTurb = 2; break;
4311  }
4312  }
4313  if (freesurface) nVar_AdjLevelSet = 1;
4314 
4315  /*--- Allocate memory for the residual ---*/
4316  residual_flow = new su2double[nVar_Flow];
4317  residual_turbulent = new su2double[nVar_Turb];
4318  residual_transition = new su2double[nVar_Trans];
4319  residual_levelset = new su2double[nVar_LevelSet];
4320  residual_wave = new su2double[nVar_Wave];
4321  residual_heat = new su2double[nVar_Heat];
4322  residual_fem = new su2double[nVar_FEM];
4323 
4324  residual_adjflow = new su2double[nVar_AdjFlow];
4325  residual_adjturbulent = new su2double[nVar_AdjTurb];
4326  residual_adjlevelset = new su2double[nVar_AdjLevelSet];
4327 
4328  /*--- Allocate memory for the coefficients being monitored ---*/
4329  aeroelastic_plunge = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];
4330  aeroelastic_pitch = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];
4331  Surface_CLift = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];
4332  Surface_CDrag = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];
4333  Surface_CSideForce = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];
4334  Surface_CEff = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];
4335  Surface_CFx = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];
4336  Surface_CFy = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];
4337  Surface_CFz = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];
4338  Surface_CMx = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];
4339  Surface_CMy = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];
4340  Surface_CMz = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];
4341 
4342  /*--- Allocate memory for the turboperformace ---*/
4343  TotalStaticEfficiency = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->Get_nMarkerTurboPerf()];
4344  TotalTotalEfficiency = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->Get_nMarkerTurboPerf()];
4345  KineticEnergyLoss = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->Get_nMarkerTurboPerf()];
4346  TotalPressureLoss = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->Get_nMarkerTurboPerf()];
4347  MassFlowIn = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->Get_nMarkerTurboPerf()];
4348  MassFlowOut = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->Get_nMarkerTurboPerf()];
4349  FlowAngleIn = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->Get_nMarkerTurboPerf()];
4350  FlowAngleOut = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->Get_nMarkerTurboPerf()];
4351  EulerianWork = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->Get_nMarkerTurboPerf()];
4352  TotalEnthalpyIn = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->Get_nMarkerTurboPerf()];
4353  PressureRatio = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->Get_nMarkerTurboPerf()];
4354  PressureOut = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->Get_nMarkerTurboPerf()];
4355  EnthalpyOut = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->Get_nMarkerTurboPerf()];
4356  MachIn = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->Get_nMarkerTurboPerf()];
4357  MachOut = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->Get_nMarkerTurboPerf()];
4358  NormalMachIn = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->Get_nMarkerTurboPerf()];
4359  NormalMachOut = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->Get_nMarkerTurboPerf()];
4360  VelocityOutIs = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->Get_nMarkerTurboPerf()];
4361 
4362  /*--- Write information from nodes ---*/
4363  switch (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver()) {
4364 
4365  case EULER: case NAVIER_STOKES: case RANS:
4366  case ADJ_EULER: case ADJ_NAVIER_STOKES: case ADJ_RANS:
4367  case DISC_ADJ_EULER: case DISC_ADJ_NAVIER_STOKES: case DISC_ADJ_RANS:
4368 
4369  /*--- Flow solution coefficients ---*/
4370  Total_CLift = solver_container[val_iZone][FinestMesh][FLOW_SOL]->GetTotal_CLift();
4371  Total_CDrag = solver_container[val_iZone][FinestMesh][FLOW_SOL]->GetTotal_CDrag();
4372  Total_CSideForce = solver_container[val_iZone][FinestMesh][FLOW_SOL]->GetTotal_CSideForce();
4373  Total_CEff = solver_container[val_iZone][FinestMesh][FLOW_SOL]->GetTotal_CEff();
4374  Total_CMx = solver_container[val_iZone][FinestMesh][FLOW_SOL]->GetTotal_CMx();
4375  Total_CMy = solver_container[val_iZone][FinestMesh][FLOW_SOL]->GetTotal_CMy();
4376  Total_CMz = solver_container[val_iZone][FinestMesh][FLOW_SOL]->GetTotal_CMz();
4377  Total_CFx = solver_container[val_iZone][FinestMesh][FLOW_SOL]->GetTotal_CFx();
4378  Total_CFy = solver_container[val_iZone][FinestMesh][FLOW_SOL]->GetTotal_CFy();
4379  Total_CFz = solver_container[val_iZone][FinestMesh][FLOW_SOL]->GetTotal_CFz();
4380 
4381  if (direct_diff != NO_DERIVATIVE){
4382  D_Total_CLift = SU2_TYPE::GetDerivative(Total_CLift);
4383  D_Total_CDrag = SU2_TYPE::GetDerivative(Total_CDrag);
4384  D_Total_CSideForce = SU2_TYPE::GetDerivative(Total_CSideForce);
4385  D_Total_CEff = SU2_TYPE::GetDerivative(Total_CEff);
4386  D_Total_CMx = SU2_TYPE::GetDerivative(Total_CMx);
4387  D_Total_CMy = SU2_TYPE::GetDerivative(Total_CMy);
4388  D_Total_CMz = SU2_TYPE::GetDerivative(Total_CMz);
4389  D_Total_CFx = SU2_TYPE::GetDerivative(Total_CFx);
4390  D_Total_CFy = SU2_TYPE::GetDerivative(Total_CFy);
4391  D_Total_CFz = SU2_TYPE::GetDerivative(Total_CFz);
4392  }
4393 
4394  if (freesurface) {
4395  Total_CFreeSurface = solver_container[val_iZone][FinestMesh][FLOW_SOL]->GetTotal_CFreeSurface();
4396  }
4397 
4398  if (isothermal) {
4399  Total_Heat = solver_container[val_iZone][FinestMesh][FLOW_SOL]->GetTotal_HeatFlux();
4400  Total_MaxHeat = solver_container[val_iZone][FinestMesh][FLOW_SOL]->GetTotal_MaxHeatFlux();

5666  delete [] Surface_CMz;
5667  delete [] aeroelastic_pitch;
5668  delete [] aeroelastic_plunge;

5691 
5692 void COutput::SetCFL_Number(CSolver ****solver_container, CConfig **config, unsigned short val_iZone) {
5693 
5694  su2double CFLFactor = 1.0, power = 1.0, CFL = 0.0, CFLMin = 0.0, CFLMax = 0.0, Div = 1.0, Diff = 0.0, MGFactor[100];
5695  unsigned short iMesh;
5696 
5697  unsigned short FinestMesh = config[val_iZone]->GetFinestMesh();
5698  unsigned long ExtIter = config[val_iZone]->GetExtIter();
5699 
5700  RhoRes_New = solver_container[val_iZone][FinestMesh][FLOW_SOL]->GetRes_RMS(0);
5701  switch( config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver()){
5702  case ADJ_EULER : case ADJ_NAVIER_STOKES: case ADJ_RANS:
5703  RhoRes_New = solver_container[val_iZone][FinestMesh][ADJFLOW_SOL]->GetRes_RMS(0);
5704  break;
5705  }
5706 
5707  if (RhoRes_New < EPS) RhoRes_New = EPS;
5708  if (RhoRes_Old < EPS) RhoRes_Old = RhoRes_New;
5709 
5710  Div = RhoRes_Old/RhoRes_New;
5711  Diff = RhoRes_New-RhoRes_Old;
5712 
5713  /*--- Compute MG factor ---*/
5714 
5715  for (iMesh = 0; iMesh <= config[val_iZone]->GetnMGLevels(); iMesh++) {
5716  if (iMesh == MESH_0) MGFactor[iMesh] = 1.0;
5717  else MGFactor[iMesh] = MGFactor[iMesh-1] * config[val_iZone]->GetCFL(iMesh)/config[val_iZone]->GetCFL(iMesh-1);
5718  }
5719 
5720  if (Div < 1.0) power = config[val_iZone]->GetCFL_AdaptParam(0);
5721  else power = config[val_iZone]->GetCFL_AdaptParam(1);
5722 
5723  /*--- Detect a stall in the residual ---*/
5724 
5725  if ((fabs(Diff) <= RhoRes_New*1E-8) && (ExtIter != 0)) { Div = 0.1; power = config[val_iZone]->GetCFL_AdaptParam(1); }
5726 
5727  CFLMin = config[val_iZone]->GetCFL_AdaptParam(2);
5728  CFLMax = config[val_iZone]->GetCFL_AdaptParam(3);
5729 
5730  CFLFactor = pow(Div, power);
5731 
5732  for (iMesh = 0; iMesh <= config[val_iZone]->GetnMGLevels(); iMesh++) {
5733  CFL = config[val_iZone]->GetCFL(iMesh);
5734  CFL *= CFLFactor;
5735 
5736  if ((iMesh == MESH_0) && (CFL <= CFLMin)) {
5737  for (iMesh = 0; iMesh <= config[val_iZone]->GetnMGLevels(); iMesh++) {
5738  config[val_iZone]->SetCFL(iMesh, 1.001*CFLMin*MGFactor[iMesh]);
5739  }
5740  break;
5741  }
5742  if ((iMesh == MESH_0) && (CFL >= CFLMax)) {
5743  for (iMesh = 0; iMesh <= config[val_iZone]->GetnMGLevels(); iMesh++)
5744  config[val_iZone]->SetCFL(iMesh, 0.999*CFLMax*MGFactor[iMesh]);
5745  break;
5746  }
5747 
5748  config[val_iZone]->SetCFL(iMesh, CFL);
5749 
5750  }
5751 
5752  RhoRes_Old = solver_container[val_iZone][FinestMesh][FLOW_SOL]->GetRes_RMS(0);
5753  switch( config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver()){
5754  case ADJ_EULER : case ADJ_NAVIER_STOKES: case ADJ_RANS:
5755  RhoRes_Old = solver_container[val_iZone][FinestMesh][ADJFLOW_SOL]->GetRes_RMS(0);
5756  break;
5757  }
5758 
5759 }
5760

5762 void COutput::SetForces_Breakdown(CGeometry ***geometry,
5763  CSolver ****solver_container,
5764  CConfig **config,
5765  CIntegration ***integration,
5766  unsigned short val_iZone) {
5767 
5768  char cstr[200];
5769  unsigned short iMarker_Monitoring;
5770  ofstream Breakdown_file;
5771 
5772  int rank = MASTER_NODE;
5773  bool compressible = (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Regime() == COMPRESSIBLE);
5774  bool incompressible = (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Regime() == INCOMPRESSIBLE);
5775  bool freesurface = (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Regime() == FREESURFACE);
5776  bool unsteady = (config[val_iZone]->GetUnsteady_Simulation() != NO);
5777  bool viscous = config[val_iZone]->GetViscous();
5778  bool grid_movement = config[val_iZone]->GetGrid_Movement();
5779  bool gravity = config[val_iZone]->GetGravityForce();
5780  bool turbulent = config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == RANS;
5781 
5782 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
5783  MPI_Comm_rank(MPI_COMM_WORLD, &rank);
5784 #endif
5785 
5786  unsigned short FinestMesh = config[val_iZone]->GetFinestMesh();
5787  unsigned short nDim = geometry[val_iZone][FinestMesh]->GetnDim();
5788  bool flow = ((config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == EULER) || (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == NAVIER_STOKES) ||
5789  (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == RANS));
5790 
5791  /*--- Output the mean flow solution using only the master node ---*/
5792 
5793  if ((rank == MASTER_NODE) && (flow)) {
5794 
5795  cout << "Writing the forces breakdown file." << endl;

5797  /*--- Initialize variables to store information from all domains (direct solution) ---*/

5810

5812  Surface_CDrag = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];

5820  Surface_CMz = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];
5821

5825  Surface_CEff_Inv = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];
5826  Surface_CFx_Inv = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];
5827  Surface_CFy_Inv = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];
5828  Surface_CFz_Inv = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];
5829  Surface_CMx_Inv = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];

5831  Surface_CMz_Inv = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];

5974  break;
5975 
5976  case VW_GAS:
5977  Breakdown_file << "Fluid Model: Van der Waals "<< "\n";
5978  Breakdown_file << "Specific gas constant: " << config[val_iZone]->GetGas_Constant() << " N.m/kg.K." << "\n";
5979  Breakdown_file << "Specific gas constant (non-dim): " << config[val_iZone]->GetGas_ConstantND()<< "\n";
5980  Breakdown_file << "Specific Heat Ratio: "<< config[val_iZone]->GetGamma() << "\n";
