5982  Breakdown_file << "Critical Temperature: " << config[val_iZone]->GetTemperature_Critical() << " K." << "\n";

5985  break;
5986 
5987  case PR_GAS:
5988  Breakdown_file << "Fluid Model: Peng-Robinson "<< "\n";
5989  Breakdown_file << "Specific gas constant: " << config[val_iZone]->GetGas_Constant() << " N.m/kg.K." << "\n";
5990  Breakdown_file << "Specific gas constant(non-dim): " << config[val_iZone]->GetGas_ConstantND()<< "\n";
5991  Breakdown_file << "Specific Heat Ratio: "<< config[val_iZone]->GetGamma() << "\n";
5992  Breakdown_file << "Critical Pressure: " << config[val_iZone]->GetPressure_Critical() << " Pa." << "\n";
5993  Breakdown_file << "Critical Temperature: " << config[val_iZone]->GetTemperature_Critical() << " K." << "\n";
5994  Breakdown_file << "Critical Pressure (non-dim): " << config[val_iZone]->GetPressure_Critical() /config[val_iZone]->GetPressure_Ref() << "\n";
5995  Breakdown_file << "Critical Temperature (non-dim) : " << config[val_iZone]->GetTemperature_Critical() /config[val_iZone]->GetTemperature_Ref() << "\n";
5996  break;
5997  }
5998 
5999  if (viscous) {
6000 
6001  switch (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_ViscosityModel()) {
6002 
6003  case CONSTANT_VISCOSITY:
6004  Breakdown_file << "Viscosity Model: CONSTANT_VISCOSITY "<< "\n";
6005  Breakdown_file << "Laminar Viscosity: " << config[val_iZone]->GetMu_ConstantND()*config[val_iZone]->GetViscosity_Ref();
6006  if (config[val_iZone]->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) Breakdown_file << " N.s/m^2." << "\n";
6007  else if (config[val_iZone]->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Breakdown_file << " lbf.s/ft^2." << "\n";
6008  Breakdown_file << "Laminar Viscosity (non-dim): " << config[val_iZone]->GetMu_ConstantND()<< "\n";
6009  break;
6010 
6011  case SUTHERLAND:

6502 void COutput::SetResult_Files(CSolver ****solver_container, CGeometry ***geometry, CConfig **config,
6503  unsigned long iExtIter, unsigned short val_nZone) {
6504 
6505  int rank = MASTER_NODE;
6506 
6507 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
6508  int size;
6509  MPI_Comm_rank(MPI_COMM_WORLD, &rank);
6510 #endif
6511 
6512  unsigned short iZone;
6513 
6514  for (iZone = 0; iZone < val_nZone; iZone++) {
6515 
6516  /*--- Flags identifying the types of files to be written. ---*/
6517 
6518  bool Wrt_Vol = config[iZone]->GetWrt_Vol_Sol();
6519  bool Wrt_Srf = config[iZone]->GetWrt_Srf_Sol();
6520 
6521 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
6522  /*--- Do not merge the volume solutions if we are running in parallel.
6523  Force the use of SU2_SOL to merge the volume sols in this case. ---*/
6524 
6525  MPI_Comm_size(MPI_COMM_WORLD, &size);
6526  if (size > SINGLE_NODE) {
6527  Wrt_Vol = false;
6528  Wrt_Srf = false;
6529  }
6530 #endif
6531 
6532  bool Wrt_Csv = config[iZone]->GetWrt_Csv_Sol();
6533 
6534  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) cout << endl << "Writing comma-separated values (CSV) surface files." << endl;
6535 
6536  switch (config[iZone]->GetKind_Solver()) {
6537 
6538  case EULER : case NAVIER_STOKES : case RANS :
6539 
6540  if (Wrt_Csv) SetSurfaceCSV_Flow(config[iZone], geometry[iZone][MESH_0], solver_container[iZone][MESH_0][FLOW_SOL], iExtIter, iZone);
6541  break;
6542 
6543  case ADJ_EULER : case ADJ_NAVIER_STOKES : case ADJ_RANS : case DISC_ADJ_EULER: case DISC_ADJ_NAVIER_STOKES: case DISC_ADJ_RANS:
6544  if (Wrt_Csv) SetSurfaceCSV_Adjoint(config[iZone], geometry[iZone][MESH_0], solver_container[iZone][MESH_0][ADJFLOW_SOL], solver_container[iZone][MESH_0][FLOW_SOL], iExtIter, iZone);
6545  break;
6546 
6547  }
6548 
6549  /*--- Get the file output format ---*/
6550 
6551  unsigned short FileFormat = config[iZone]->GetOutput_FileFormat();
6552 
6553  /*--- Merge the node coordinates and connectivity, if necessary. This
6554  is only performed if a volume solution file is requested, and it
6555  is active by default. ---*/
6556 
6557  if (Wrt_Vol || Wrt_Srf) {
6558  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) cout << "Merging connectivities in the Master node." << endl;
6559  MergeConnectivity(config[iZone], geometry[iZone][MESH_0], iZone);
6560  }
6561 
6562  /*--- Merge coordinates of all grid nodes (excluding ghost points).
6563  The grid coordinates are always merged and included first in the
6564  restart files. ---*/
6565 
6566  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) cout << "Merging coordinates in the Master node." << endl;
6567  MergeCoordinates(config[iZone], geometry[iZone][MESH_0]);
6568 
6569  if ((rank == MASTER_NODE) && (Wrt_Vol || Wrt_Srf)) {
6570  if (FileFormat == TECPLOT_BINARY) {
6571  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) cout << "Writing Tecplot binary volume and surface mesh files." << endl;
6572  SetTecplotBinary_DomainMesh(config[iZone], geometry[iZone][MESH_0], iZone);
6573  SetTecplotBinary_SurfaceMesh(config[iZone], geometry[iZone][MESH_0], iZone);
6574  if (!wrote_base_file)
6575  DeallocateConnectivity(config[iZone], geometry[iZone][MESH_0], false);
6576  if (!wrote_surf_file)
6577  DeallocateConnectivity(config[iZone], geometry[iZone][MESH_0], wrote_surf_file);
6578  }
6579  }
6580 
6581  /*--- Merge the solution data needed for volume solutions and restarts ---*/
6582 
6583  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) cout << "Merging solution in the Master node." << endl;
6584  MergeSolution(config[iZone], geometry[iZone][MESH_0], solver_container[iZone][MESH_0], iZone);
6585 
6586  /*--- Write restart, or Tecplot files using the merged data.
6587  This data lives only on the master, and these routines are currently
6588  executed by the master proc alone (as if in serial). ---*/
6589 
6590  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) {
6591 
6592  /*--- Write a native restart file ---*/
6593 
6594  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) cout << "Writing SU2 native restart file." << endl;
6595  SetRestart(config[iZone], geometry[iZone][MESH_0], solver_container[iZone][MESH_0] , iZone);
6596 
6597  if (Wrt_Vol) {
6598 
6599  switch (FileFormat) {
6600 
6601  case TECPLOT:
6602 
6603  /*--- Write a Tecplot ASCII file ---*/
6604 
6605  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) cout << "Writing Tecplot ASCII file volume solution file." << endl;
6606  SetTecplotASCII(config[iZone], geometry[iZone][MESH_0], solver_container[iZone][MESH_0], iZone, val_nZone, false);
6607  DeallocateConnectivity(config[iZone], geometry[iZone][MESH_0], false);
6608  break;
6609 
6610  case FIELDVIEW:
6611 
6612  /*--- Write a FieldView ASCII file ---*/
6613 
6614  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) cout << "Writing FieldView ASCII file volume solution file." << endl;
6615  SetFieldViewASCII(config[iZone], geometry[iZone][MESH_0], iZone, val_nZone);
6616  DeallocateConnectivity(config[iZone], geometry[iZone][MESH_0], false);
6617  break;
6618 
6619  case TECPLOT_BINARY:
6620 
6621  /*--- Write a Tecplot binary solution file ---*/
6622 
6623  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) cout << "Writing Tecplot binary volume solution file." << endl;
6624  SetTecplotBinary_DomainSolution(config[iZone], geometry[iZone][MESH_0], iZone);
6625  break;
6626 
6627  case FIELDVIEW_BINARY:
6628 
6629  /*--- Write a FieldView binary file ---*/
6630 
6631  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) cout << "Writing FieldView binary file volume solution file." << endl;
6632  SetFieldViewBinary(config[iZone], geometry[iZone][MESH_0], iZone, val_nZone);
6633  DeallocateConnectivity(config[iZone], geometry[iZone][MESH_0], false);
6634  break;
6635 
6636  case PARAVIEW:
6637 
6638  /*--- Write a Paraview ASCII file ---*/
6639 
6640  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) cout << "Writing Paraview ASCII volume solution file." << endl;
6641  SetParaview_ASCII(config[iZone], geometry[iZone][MESH_0], iZone, val_nZone, false);
6642  DeallocateConnectivity(config[iZone], geometry[iZone][MESH_0], false);
6643  break;
6644 
6645  default:
6646  break;
6647  }
6648 
6649  }
6650 
6651  if (Wrt_Srf) {
6652 
6653  switch (FileFormat) {
6654 
6655  case TECPLOT:
6656 
6657  /*--- Write a Tecplot ASCII file ---*/
6658 
6659  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) cout << "Writing Tecplot ASCII surface solution file." << endl;
6660  SetTecplotASCII(config[iZone], geometry[iZone][MESH_0], solver_container[iZone][MESH_0] , iZone, val_nZone, true);
6661  DeallocateConnectivity(config[iZone], geometry[iZone][MESH_0], true);
6662  break;
6663 
6664  case TECPLOT_BINARY:
6665 
6666  /*--- Write a Tecplot binary solution file ---*/
6667 
6668  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) cout << "Writing Tecplot binary surface solution file." << endl;
6669  SetTecplotBinary_SurfaceSolution(config[iZone], geometry[iZone][MESH_0], iZone);
6670  break;
6671 
6672  case PARAVIEW:
6673 
6674  /*--- Write a Paraview ASCII file ---*/
6675 
6676  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) cout << "Writing Paraview ASCII surface solution file." << endl;
6677  SetParaview_ASCII(config[iZone], geometry[iZone][MESH_0], iZone, val_nZone, true);
6678  DeallocateConnectivity(config[iZone], geometry[iZone][MESH_0], true);
6679  break;
6680 
6681  default:
6682  break;
6683  }
6684 
6685  }
6686 
6687  /*--- Release memory needed for merging the solution data. ---*/
6688 
6689  DeallocateCoordinates(config[iZone], geometry[iZone][MESH_0]);
6690  DeallocateSolution(config[iZone], geometry[iZone][MESH_0]);
6691 
6692  }
6693 
6694  /*--- Final broadcast (informing other procs that the base output
6695  file was written). ---*/
6696 
6697 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
6698  SU2_MPI::Bcast(&wrote_base_file, 1, MPI_UNSIGNED_SHORT, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
6699  SU2_MPI::Bcast(&wrote_surf_file, 1, MPI_UNSIGNED_SHORT, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
6700 #endif
6701 
6702  }
6703 }

6705 void COutput::SetBaselineResult_Files(CSolver **solver, CGeometry **geometry, CConfig **config,
6706  unsigned long iExtIter, unsigned short val_nZone) {
6707 
6708  int rank = MASTER_NODE;
6709  int size = SINGLE_NODE;
6710 
6711 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
6712  MPI_Comm_rank(MPI_COMM_WORLD, &rank);
6713  MPI_Comm_size(MPI_COMM_WORLD, &size);
6714 #endif
6715 
6716  unsigned short iZone;
6717 
6718  for (iZone = 0; iZone < val_nZone; iZone++) {
6719 
6720  /*--- Flags identifying the types of files to be written. ---*/
6721 
6722  bool Low_MemoryOutput = config[iZone]->GetLow_MemoryOutput();
6723  bool Wrt_Vol = config[iZone]->GetWrt_Vol_Sol();
6724  bool Wrt_Srf = config[iZone]->GetWrt_Srf_Sol();
6725 
6726  /*--- Get the file output format ---*/
6727 
6728  unsigned short FileFormat = config[iZone]->GetOutput_FileFormat();
6729 
6730  /*--- Merge the node coordinates and connectivity if necessary. This
6731  is only performed if a volume solution file is requested, and it
6732  is active by default. ---*/
6733 
6734  if ((Wrt_Vol || Wrt_Srf) && (!Low_MemoryOutput)) {
6735  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) cout << "Merging connectivities in the Master node." << endl;
6736  MergeConnectivity(config[iZone], geometry[iZone], iZone);
6737  }
6738 
6739  /*--- Merge the solution data needed for volume solutions and restarts ---*/
6740 
6741  if ((Wrt_Vol || Wrt_Srf) && (!Low_MemoryOutput)) {
6742  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) cout << "Merging solution in the Master node." << endl;
6743  MergeBaselineSolution(config[iZone], geometry[iZone], solver[iZone], iZone);
6744  }
6745 
6746  /*--- Write restart, Tecplot or Paraview files using the merged data.
6747  This data lives only on the master, and these routines are currently
6748  executed by the master proc alone (as if in serial). ---*/
6749 
6750  if (!Low_MemoryOutput) {
6751 
6752  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) {
6753 
6754  if (Wrt_Vol) {
6755 
6756  switch (FileFormat) {
6757 
6758  case TECPLOT:
6759 
6760  /*--- Write a Tecplot ASCII file ---*/
6761 
6762  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) cout << "Writing Tecplot ASCII file (volume grid)." << endl;
6763  SetTecplotASCII(config[iZone], geometry[iZone], solver, iZone, val_nZone, false);
6764  DeallocateConnectivity(config[iZone], geometry[iZone], false);
6765  break;
6766 
6767  case FIELDVIEW:
6768 
6769  /*--- Write a FieldView ASCII file ---*/
6770 
6771  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) cout << "Writing FieldView ASCII file (volume grid)." << endl;
6772  SetFieldViewASCII(config[iZone], geometry[iZone], iZone, val_nZone);
6773  DeallocateConnectivity(config[iZone], geometry[iZone], false);
6774  break;
6775 
6776  case TECPLOT_BINARY:
6777 
6778  /*--- Write a Tecplot binary solution file ---*/
6779 
6780  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) cout << "Writing Tecplot Binary file (volume grid)." << endl;
6781  SetTecplotBinary_DomainMesh(config[iZone], geometry[iZone], iZone);
6782  SetTecplotBinary_DomainSolution(config[iZone], geometry[iZone], iZone);
6783  break;
6784 
6785  case FIELDVIEW_BINARY:
6786 
6787  /*--- Write a binary binary file ---*/
6788 
6789  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) cout << "Writing FieldView ASCII file (volume grid)." << endl;
6790  SetFieldViewBinary(config[iZone], geometry[iZone], iZone, val_nZone);
6791  DeallocateConnectivity(config[iZone], geometry[iZone], false);
6792  break;
6793 
6794  case PARAVIEW:
6795 
6796  /*--- Write a Paraview ASCII file ---*/
6797 
6798  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) cout << "Writing Paraview ASCII file (volume grid)." << endl;
6799  SetParaview_ASCII(config[iZone], geometry[iZone], iZone, val_nZone, false);
6800  DeallocateConnectivity(config[iZone], geometry[iZone], false);
6801  break;
6802 
6803  default:
6804  break;
6805  }
6806 
6807  }
6808 
6809  if (Wrt_Srf) {
6810 
6811  switch (FileFormat) {
6812 
6813  case TECPLOT:
6814 
6815  /*--- Write a Tecplot ASCII file ---*/
6816 
6817  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) cout << "Writing Tecplot ASCII file (surface grid)." << endl;
6818  SetTecplotASCII(config[iZone], geometry[iZone], solver, iZone, val_nZone, true);
6819  DeallocateConnectivity(config[iZone], geometry[iZone], true);
6820  break;
6821 
6822  case TECPLOT_BINARY:
6823 
6824  /*--- Write a Tecplot binary solution file ---*/
6825 
6826  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) cout << "Writing Tecplot Binary file (surface grid)." << endl;
6827  SetTecplotBinary_SurfaceMesh(config[iZone], geometry[iZone], iZone);
6828  SetTecplotBinary_SurfaceSolution(config[iZone], geometry[iZone], iZone);
6829  break;
6830 
6831  case PARAVIEW:
6832 
6833  /*--- Write a Paraview ASCII file ---*/
6834 
6835  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) cout << "Writing Paraview ASCII file (surface grid)." << endl;
6836  SetParaview_ASCII(config[iZone], geometry[iZone], iZone, val_nZone, true);
6837  DeallocateConnectivity(config[iZone], geometry[iZone], true);
6838  break;
6839 
6840  default:
6841  break;
6842  }
6843  }
6844 
6845  if (FileFormat == TECPLOT_BINARY) {
6846  if (!wrote_base_file)
6847  DeallocateConnectivity(config[iZone], geometry[iZone], false);
6848  if (!wrote_surf_file)
6849  DeallocateConnectivity(config[iZone], geometry[iZone], wrote_surf_file);
6850  }
6851 
6852  if (Wrt_Vol || Wrt_Srf)
6853  DeallocateSolution(config[iZone], geometry[iZone]);
6854  }
6855 
6856  }
6857 
6858  else {
6859 
6860  if (Wrt_Vol) {
6861 
6862  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) cout << "Writing Tecplot ASCII file (volume grid)." << endl;
6863  char buffer_char[50], out_file[MAX_STRING_SIZE];
6864 
6865  string filename;
6866  if (!config[iZone]->GetContinuous_Adjoint()) filename = config[iZone]->GetFlow_FileName();
6867  else filename = config[iZone]->GetAdj_FileName();
6868 
6869  if (size > 1) {
6870  SPRINTF (buffer_char, "_%d", SU2_TYPE::Int(rank+1));
6871  filename = filename + buffer_char;
6872  }
6873 
6874  SPRINTF (buffer_char, ".dat");
6875  strcpy(out_file, filename.c_str()); strcat(out_file, buffer_char);
6876  SetTecplotASCII_LowMemory(config[iZone], geometry[iZone], solver, out_file, false);
6877  }
6878 
6879  if (Wrt_Srf) {
6880 
6881  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) cout << "Writing Tecplot ASCII file (surface grid)." << endl;
6882  char buffer_char[50], out_file[MAX_STRING_SIZE];
6883 
6884  string filename;
6885  if (!config[iZone]->GetContinuous_Adjoint()) filename = config[iZone]->GetSurfFlowCoeff_FileName();
6886  else filename = config[iZone]->GetSurfAdjCoeff_FileName();
6887 
6888  if (size > 1) {
6889  SPRINTF (buffer_char, "_%d", SU2_TYPE::Int(rank+1));
6890  filename = filename + buffer_char;
6891  }
6892 
6893  SPRINTF (buffer_char, ".dat");
6894  strcpy(out_file, filename.c_str()); strcat(out_file, buffer_char);
6895  SetTecplotASCII_LowMemory(config[iZone], geometry[iZone], solver, out_file, true);
6896  }
6897 
6898  }
6899 
6900  /*--- Final broadcast (informing other procs that the base output
6901  file was written). ---*/
6902 
6903 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
6904  SU2_MPI::Bcast(&wrote_base_file, 1, MPI_UNSIGNED_SHORT, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
6905 #endif
6906 
6907  }
6908 }

6910 void COutput::SetMesh_Files(CGeometry **geometry, CConfig **config, unsigned short val_nZone, bool new_file, bool su2_file) {
6911 
6912  int rank = MASTER_NODE;
6913 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
6914  MPI_Comm_rank(MPI_COMM_WORLD, &rank);
6915 #endif
6916 
6917  unsigned short iZone;
6918 
6919  for (iZone = 0; iZone < val_nZone; iZone++) {
6920 
6921  /*--- Flags identifying the types of files to be written. ---*/
6922 
6923  bool Wrt_Vol = config[iZone]->GetWrt_Vol_Sol() && config[iZone]->GetVisualize_Deformation();
6924  bool Wrt_Srf = config[iZone]->GetWrt_Srf_Sol() && config[iZone]->GetVisualize_Deformation();;
6925 
6926  /*--- Merge the node coordinates and connectivity if necessary. This
6927  is only performed if a volume solution file is requested, and it
6928  is active by default. ---*/
6929 
6930  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) cout <<"Merging grid connectivity." << endl;
6931  MergeConnectivity(config[iZone], geometry[iZone], iZone);
6932 
6933  /*--- Merge coordinates of all grid nodes (excluding ghost points).
6934  The grid coordinates are always merged and included first in the
6935  restart files. ---*/
6936 
6937  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) cout <<"Merging grid coordinates." << endl;
6938  MergeCoordinates(config[iZone], geometry[iZone]);
6939 
6940  /*--- Write restart, Tecplot or Paraview files using the merged data.
6941  This data lives only on the master, and these routines are currently
6942  executed by the master proc alone (as if in serial). ---*/
6943 
6944  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) {
6945 
6946  if (Wrt_Vol) {
6947 
6948  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) cout <<"Writing volume mesh file." << endl;
6949 
6950  /*--- Write a Tecplot ASCII file ---*/
6951  if (config[iZone]->GetOutput_FileFormat()==PARAVIEW) SetParaview_MeshASCII(config[iZone], geometry[iZone], iZone, val_nZone, false,new_file);
6952  else SetTecplotASCII_Mesh(config[iZone], geometry[iZone], false, new_file);
6953 
6954  }
6955 
6956  if (Wrt_Srf) {
6957 
6958  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) cout <<"Writing surface mesh file." << endl;
6959 
6960  /*--- Write a Tecplot ASCII file ---*/
6961  if (config[iZone]->GetOutput_FileFormat()==PARAVIEW) SetParaview_MeshASCII(config[iZone], geometry[iZone], iZone, val_nZone, true,new_file);
6962  else SetTecplotASCII_Mesh(config[iZone], geometry[iZone], true, new_file);
6963 
6964 
6965  }
6966 
6967  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) cout <<"Writing .su2 file." << endl;
6968 
6969  /*--- Write a .su2 ASCII file ---*/
6970 
6971  if (su2_file) SetSU2_MeshASCII(config[iZone], geometry[iZone]);
6972 
6973  /*--- Deallocate connectivity ---*/
6974 
6975  DeallocateConnectivity(config[iZone], geometry[iZone], true);
6976 
6977  }
6978 
6979  /*--- Final broadcast (informing other procs that the base output
6980  file was written). ---*/
6981 
6982 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
6983  SU2_MPI::Bcast(&wrote_base_file, 1, MPI_UNSIGNED_SHORT, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
6984 #endif
6985 
6986  }
6987 }

6989 void COutput::SetMassFlowRate(CSolver *solver_container, CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config) {
6990  unsigned short iDim, iMarker_monitor, iMarker;
6991  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint;
6992  su2double Vector[3], Total_Mdot=0.0;
6993  unsigned short nDim = geometry->GetnDim();
6994 
6995  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker< config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
6996  iMarker_monitor = config->GetMarker_All_Monitoring(iMarker);
6997  if (iMarker_monitor){
6998  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[ iMarker ]; iVertex++) {
6999  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
7000 
7001  if (geometry->node[iPoint]->GetDomain()) {
7002  geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Vector);
7003 
7004  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7005  Total_Mdot -= Vector[iDim]*(solver_container->node[iPoint]->GetSolution(iDim+1));
7006  }
7007  }
7008  }
7009  }
7010 
7011 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
7012  /*--- Add AllBound information using all the nodes ---*/
7013  su2double My_Total_Mdot = Total_Mdot; Total_Mdot = 0.0;
7014  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&My_Total_Mdot, &Total_Mdot, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
7015 #endif
7016  /*--- Set the output: reusing same variable from OneDimensionalOutput code ---*/
7017  solver_container->SetOneD_MassFlowRate(Total_Mdot);
7018 }
7019 
7020 void COutput::OneDimensionalOutput(CSolver *solver_container, CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config) {
7021 
7022  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint;
7023  unsigned short iDim, iMarker, Out1D;
7024  su2double *Normal = NULL, Area = 0.0, UnitNormal[3],
7025  Tot_Pressure, Mach, Temperature, Pressure = 0.0, Velocity2, Enthalpy, RhoUA, U,// local values at each node (Velocity2 = V^2). U = normal velocity
7026  AveragePt = 0.0, AverageMach = 0.0, AverageTemperature = 0.0, MassFlowRate = 0.0, // Area Averaged value ( sum / A )
7027  VelocityRef = 0.0, EnthalpyRef = 0.0, DensityRef = 0.0, PressureRef = 0.0; // Flux conserved values. TemperatureRef follows ideal gas
7028  su2double TotalArea=0.0;
7029 
7030  bool compressible = (config->GetKind_Regime() == COMPRESSIBLE);
7031  bool incompressible = (config->GetKind_Regime() == INCOMPRESSIBLE);
7032  bool freesurface = (config->GetKind_Regime() == FREESURFACE);
7033  su2double Gamma = config->GetGamma();
7034  unsigned short nDim = geometry->GetnDim();
7035 
7036 
7037  /*--- Loop over the markers ---*/
7038 
7039  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
7040 
7041  Out1D = config->GetMarker_All_Out_1D(iMarker);
7042 
7043  /*--- Loop over the vertices to compute the output ---*/
7044 
7045 
7046  if (Out1D == YES) {
7047 
7048  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->GetnVertex(iMarker); iVertex++) {
7049 
7050  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
7051 
7052  /*--- Find the normal direction ---*/
7053 
7054  if (geometry->node[iPoint]->GetDomain()) {
7055 
7056 
7057  /*--- Compute area, and unitary normal ---*/
7058  Normal = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal();
7059  Area = 0.0; for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Area += Normal[iDim]*Normal[iDim]; Area = sqrt(Area);
7060  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) UnitNormal[iDim] = -Normal[iDim]/Area;
7061 
7062  if (compressible) Pressure = solver_container->node[iPoint]->GetPressure();
7063  if (incompressible || freesurface) Pressure = solver_container->node[iPoint]->GetPressureInc();
7064 
7065  /*-- Find velocity normal to the marked surface/opening --*/
7066 
7067  U = 0.0; RhoUA = 0.0;
7068  for (iDim = 0; iDim < geometry->GetnDim(); iDim++) {
7069  U += UnitNormal[iDim]*solver_container->node[iPoint]->GetVelocity(iDim);
7070  RhoUA -=Normal[iDim]*solver_container->node[iPoint]->GetSolution(iDim+1);
7071  }
7072 
7073  Enthalpy = solver_container->node[iPoint]->GetEnthalpy();
7074  Velocity2 = solver_container->node[iPoint]->GetVelocity2();
7075  Temperature = solver_container->node[iPoint]->GetTemperature();
7076 
7077  Mach = (sqrt(Velocity2))/ solver_container->node[iPoint]->GetSoundSpeed();
7078  if (incompressible)
7079  Tot_Pressure = Pressure + 0.5*solver_container->node[iPoint]->GetDensity()*Velocity2;
7080  else
7081  Tot_Pressure = Pressure*pow((1.0+((Gamma-1.0)/2.0)*pow(Mach, 2.0)),( Gamma/(Gamma-1.0) ) );
7082 
7083 
7084  AveragePt += Tot_Pressure * Area;
7085  TotalArea += Area;
7086  AverageMach += Mach*Area;
7087  PressureRef += Pressure * Area;
7088  AverageTemperature += Temperature*Area;
7089  MassFlowRate += RhoUA; // RhoU is rho * vn * Area
7090  VelocityRef+=RhoUA*U*U; // rho u A
7091  EnthalpyRef+=RhoUA*Enthalpy;
7092 
7093  }
7094  }
7095 
7096  }
7097 
7098  }
7099 
7100 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
7101 
7102  /*--- Add AllBound information using all the nodes ---*/
7103 
7104  su2double My_Area = TotalArea; TotalArea = 0.0;
7105  su2double My_AveragePt = AveragePt; AveragePt = 0.0;
7106  su2double My_AverageMach = AverageMach; AverageMach = 0.0;
7107  su2double My_AverageTemperature = AverageTemperature; AverageTemperature = 0.0;
7108  su2double My_MassFlowRate = MassFlowRate; MassFlowRate = 0.0;
7109  su2double My_PressureRef = PressureRef; PressureRef = 0.0;
7110  su2double My_VelocityRef = VelocityRef; VelocityRef = 0.0;
7111  su2double My_EnthalpyRef = EnthalpyRef; EnthalpyRef = 0.0;
7112  su2double My_DensityRef = DensityRef; DensityRef = 0.0;
7113 
7114  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&My_Area, &TotalArea, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
7115  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&My_AveragePt, &AveragePt, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
7116  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&My_AverageMach, &AverageMach, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
7117  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&My_AverageTemperature, &AverageTemperature, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
7118  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&My_MassFlowRate, &MassFlowRate, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
7119  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&My_PressureRef, &PressureRef, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
7120  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&My_VelocityRef, &VelocityRef, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
7121  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&My_EnthalpyRef , &EnthalpyRef , 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
7122  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&My_DensityRef , &DensityRef , 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
7123 
7124 #endif
7125 
7126  /*--- Set the 1D output ---*/
7127  /*--- DensityRef depends on the final values of other flux avg variables ---*/
7128  VelocityRef=sqrt(VelocityRef/MassFlowRate);
7129  PressureRef=PressureRef/TotalArea;
7130  EnthalpyRef=EnthalpyRef/MassFlowRate;
7131  DensityRef =PressureRef*Gamma/(Gamma-1)/(EnthalpyRef-0.5*VelocityRef*VelocityRef);
7132 
7133  /*Area averaged values*/
7134  solver_container->SetOneD_TotalPress(AveragePt/TotalArea);
7135  solver_container->SetOneD_Mach(AverageMach/TotalArea);
7136  solver_container->SetOneD_Temp(AverageTemperature/TotalArea);
7137  solver_container->SetOneD_MassFlowRate(MassFlowRate);
7138 
7139  /*Flux averaged values*/
7140  solver_container->SetOneD_FluxAvgPress(PressureRef);
7141  solver_container->SetOneD_FluxAvgDensity(DensityRef);
7142  solver_container->SetOneD_FluxAvgVelocity(VelocityRef);
7143  solver_container->SetOneD_FluxAvgEntalpy(EnthalpyRef);
7144 
7145 }
7146 
7147 void COutput::SetForceSections(CSolver *solver_container, CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config, unsigned long iExtIter) {
7148 
7149  short iSection, nSection;
7150  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint;
7151  su2double *Plane_P0, *Plane_Normal, MinPlane, MaxPlane, *CPressure, MinXCoord, MaxXCoord, Force[3], ForceInviscid[3],
7152  MomentInviscid[3] = {0.0,0.0,0.0}, MomentDist[3] = {0.0,0.0,0.0}, RefDensity, RefPressure, RefAreaCoeff, *Velocity_Inf, Gas_Constant, Mach2Vel, Mach_Motion, Gamma, RefVel2 = 0.0, factor, NDPressure, *Origin, RefLengthMoment, Alpha, Beta, CDrag_Inv, CLift_Inv, CMy_Inv;
7153  vector<su2double> Xcoord_Airfoil, Ycoord_Airfoil, Zcoord_Airfoil, Pressure_Airfoil;
7154  string Marker_Tag, Slice_Filename, Slice_Ext;
7155  ofstream Cp_File;
7156  unsigned short iDim;
7157 
7158  bool grid_movement = config->GetGrid_Movement();
7159  bool compressible = (config->GetKind_Regime() == COMPRESSIBLE);
7160  bool incompressible = (config->GetKind_Regime() == INCOMPRESSIBLE);
7161  bool freesurface = (config->GetKind_Regime() == FREESURFACE);
7162 
7163  Plane_P0 = new su2double [3];
7164  Plane_Normal = new su2double [3];
7165  CPressure = new su2double[geometry->GetnPoint()];
7166 
7167  /*--- Compute some reference quantities and necessary values ---*/
7168  RefDensity = solver_container->GetDensity_Inf();
7169  RefPressure = solver_container->GetPressure_Inf();
7170  RefAreaCoeff = config->GetRefAreaCoeff();
7171  Velocity_Inf = solver_container->GetVelocity_Inf();
7172  Gamma = config->GetGamma();
7173  Origin = config->GetRefOriginMoment(0);
7174  RefLengthMoment = config->GetRefLengthMoment();
7175  Alpha = config->GetAoA()*PI_NUMBER/180.0;
7176  Beta = config->GetAoS()*PI_NUMBER/180.0;
7177 
7178  if (grid_movement) {
7179  Gas_Constant = config->GetGas_ConstantND();
7180  Mach2Vel = sqrt(Gamma*Gas_Constant*config->GetTemperature_FreeStreamND());
7181  Mach_Motion = config->GetMach_Motion();
7182  RefVel2 = (Mach_Motion*Mach2Vel)*(Mach_Motion*Mach2Vel);
7183  }
7184  else {
7185  RefVel2 = 0.0;
7186  for (iDim = 0; iDim < geometry->GetnDim(); iDim++)
7187  RefVel2 += Velocity_Inf[iDim]*Velocity_Inf[iDim];
7188  }
7189  factor = 1.0 / (0.5*RefDensity*RefAreaCoeff*RefVel2);
7190 
7191  int rank = MASTER_NODE;
7192 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
7193  MPI_Comm_rank(MPI_COMM_WORLD, &rank);
7194 #endif
7195 
7196  if (geometry->GetnDim() == 3) {
7197 
7198  /*--- Copy the pressure to an auxiliar structure ---*/
7199 
7200  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < geometry->GetnPoint(); iPoint++) {
7201  if (compressible) {
7202  CPressure[iPoint] = (solver_container->node[iPoint]->GetPressure() - RefPressure)*factor*RefAreaCoeff;
7203  }
7204  if (incompressible || freesurface) {
7205  CPressure[iPoint] = (solver_container->node[iPoint]->GetPressureInc() - RefPressure)*factor*RefAreaCoeff;
7206  }
7207  }
7208 
7209  nSection = config->GetnSections();
7210 
7211  for (iSection = 0; iSection < nSection; iSection++) {
7212 
7213  /*--- Read the values from the config file ---*/
7214 
7215  MinPlane = config->GetSection_Location(0); MaxPlane = config->GetSection_Location(1);
7216  MinXCoord = -1E6; MaxXCoord = 1E6;
7217 
7218  Plane_Normal[0] = 0.0; Plane_P0[0] = 0.0;
7219  Plane_Normal[1] = 0.0; Plane_P0[1] = 0.0;
7220  Plane_Normal[2] = 0.0; Plane_P0[2] = 0.0;
7221 
7222  Plane_Normal[config->GetAxis_Orientation()] = 1.0;
7223  Plane_P0[config->GetAxis_Orientation()] = MinPlane + iSection*(MaxPlane - MinPlane)/su2double(nSection-1);
7224 
7225  /*--- Compute the airfoil sections (note that we feed in the Cp) ---*/
7226 
7227  geometry->ComputeAirfoil_Section(Plane_P0, Plane_Normal,
7228  MinXCoord, MaxXCoord, CPressure,
7229  Xcoord_Airfoil, Ycoord_Airfoil,
7230  Zcoord_Airfoil, Pressure_Airfoil, true,
7231  config);
7232 
7233  if ((rank == MASTER_NODE) && (Xcoord_Airfoil.size() == 0)) {
7234  cout << "Please check the config file, the section "<< iSection+1 <<" has not been detected." << endl;
7235  }
7236 
7237  /*--- Output the pressure on each section (tecplot format) ---*/
7238 
7239  if ((rank == MASTER_NODE) && (Xcoord_Airfoil.size() != 0)) {
7240 
7241  /*--- Write Cp at each section ---*/
7242 
7243  ofstream Cp_File;
7244  if (iSection == 0) {
7245  Cp_File.open("cp_sections.dat", ios::out);
7246  Cp_File << "TITLE = \"Airfoil sections\"" << "\n";
7247  Cp_File << "VARIABLES = \"X\",\"Y\",\"Z\",\"Cp\"" << "\n";
7248  }
7249  else Cp_File.open("cp_sections.dat", ios::app);
7250 
7251  Cp_File << "ZONE T=\"SECTION_"<< (iSection+1) << "\", NODES= "<< Xcoord_Airfoil.size() << ", ELEMENTS= " << Xcoord_Airfoil.size()-1 << ", DATAPACKING= POINT, ZONETYPE= FELINESEG" << "\n";
7252 
7253  /*--- Coordinates and pressure value ---*/
7254 
7255  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) {
7256  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < Xcoord_Airfoil.size(); iVertex++) {
7257  Cp_File << Xcoord_Airfoil[iVertex] <<" "<< Ycoord_Airfoil[iVertex] <<" "<< Zcoord_Airfoil[iVertex] <<" "<< Pressure_Airfoil[iVertex] << "\n";
7258  }
7259  }
7260  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) {
7261  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < Xcoord_Airfoil.size(); iVertex++) {
7262  Cp_File << Xcoord_Airfoil[iVertex]*12.0 <<" "<< Ycoord_Airfoil[iVertex]*12.0 <<" "<< Zcoord_Airfoil[iVertex]*12.0 <<" "<< Pressure_Airfoil[iVertex] << "\n";
7263  }
7264  }
7265 
7266  /*--- Basic conectivity ---*/
7267 
7268  for (iVertex = 1; iVertex < Xcoord_Airfoil.size(); iVertex++) {
7269  Cp_File << iVertex << "\t" << iVertex+1 << "\n";
7270  }
7271 
7272  Cp_File.close();
7273 
7274 
7275  /*--- Compute load distribution ---*/
7276 
7277  ForceInviscid[0] = 0.0; ForceInviscid[1] = 0.0; ForceInviscid[2] = 0.0; MomentInviscid[1] = 0.0;
7278 
7279  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < Xcoord_Airfoil.size()-1; iVertex++) {
7280 
7281  NDPressure = 0.5*(Pressure_Airfoil[iVertex]+Pressure_Airfoil[iVertex+1]);
7282 
7283  Force[0] = -(Zcoord_Airfoil[iVertex+1] - Zcoord_Airfoil[iVertex])*NDPressure;
7284  Force[1] = 0.0;
7285  Force[2] = (Xcoord_Airfoil[iVertex+1] - Xcoord_Airfoil[iVertex])*NDPressure;
7286 
7287  ForceInviscid[0] += Force[0];
7288  ForceInviscid[1] += Force[1];
7289  ForceInviscid[2] += Force[2];
7290 
7291  MomentDist[0] = 0.5*(Xcoord_Airfoil[iVertex] + Xcoord_Airfoil[iVertex+1]) - Origin[0];
7292  MomentDist[1] = 0.5*(Ycoord_Airfoil[iVertex] + Ycoord_Airfoil[iVertex+1]) - Origin[1];
7293  MomentDist[2] = 0.5*(Zcoord_Airfoil[iVertex] + Zcoord_Airfoil[iVertex+1]) - Origin[3];
7294 
7295  MomentInviscid[1] += (Force[0]*MomentDist[2]-Force[2]*MomentDist[0])/RefLengthMoment;
7296 
7297  }
7298 
7299  CLift_Inv = fabs( -ForceInviscid[0]*sin(Alpha) + ForceInviscid[2]*cos(Alpha));
7300  CDrag_Inv = fabs( ForceInviscid[0]*cos(Alpha)*cos(Beta) + ForceInviscid[1]*sin(Beta) + ForceInviscid[2]*sin(Alpha)*cos(Beta));
7301  CMy_Inv = MomentInviscid[1];
7302 
7303 
7304  /*--- Write load distribution ---*/
7305 
7306  ofstream Load_File;
7307  if (iSection == 0) {
7308  Load_File.open("load_distribution.dat", ios::out);
7309  Load_File << "TITLE = \"Load distribution\"" << "\n";
7310  Load_File << "VARIABLES = \"Y\",\"C<sub>L</sub>\",\"C<sub>D</sub>\",\"C<supb>My</sub>\"" << "\n";
7311  Load_File << "ZONE T=\"Wing load distribution\", NODES= "<< nSection << ", ELEMENTS= " << nSection-1 << ", DATAPACKING= POINT, ZONETYPE= FELINESEG" << "\n";
7312  }
7313  else Load_File.open("load_distribution.dat", ios::app);
7314 
7315  /*--- Coordinates and pressure value ---*/
7316 
7317  Load_File << Ycoord_Airfoil[0] <<" "<< CLift_Inv <<" "<< CDrag_Inv <<" "<< CMy_Inv << "\n";
7318 
7319  /*--- Basic conectivity ---*/
7320 
7321  if (iSection == nSection-1) {
7322  for (iSection = 1; iSection < nSection; iSection++) {
7323  Load_File << iSection << "\t" << iSection+1 << "\n";
7324  }
7325  }
7326 
7327  Load_File.close();
7328 
7329 
7330  }
7331 
7332  }
7333 
7334 
7335  }
7336 
7337  /*--- Delete dynamically allocated memory ---*/
7338 
7339  delete [] Plane_P0;
7340  delete [] Plane_Normal;
7341  delete [] CPressure;
7342 
7343 }
7344 
7345 void COutput::SetCp_InverseDesign(CSolver *solver_container, CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config, unsigned long iExtIter) {
7346 
7347  unsigned short iMarker, icommas, Boundary, iDim;
7348  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint, (*Point2Vertex)[2], nPointLocal = 0, nPointGlobal = 0;
7349  su2double XCoord, YCoord, ZCoord, Pressure, PressureCoeff = 0, Cp, CpTarget, *Normal = NULL, Area, PressDiff;
7350  bool *PointInDomain;
7351  string text_line, surfCp_filename;
7352  ifstream Surface_file;
7353  char buffer[50], cstr[200];
7354 
7355 
7356  nPointLocal = geometry->GetnPoint();
7357 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
7358  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&nPointLocal, &nPointGlobal, 1, MPI_UNSIGNED_LONG, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
7359 #else
7360  nPointGlobal = nPointLocal;
7361 #endif
7362 
7363  Point2Vertex = new unsigned long[nPointGlobal][2];
7364  PointInDomain = new bool[nPointGlobal];
7365 
7366  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointGlobal; iPoint ++)
7367  PointInDomain[iPoint] = false;
7368 
7369  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
7370  Boundary = config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker);
7371 
7372  if ((Boundary == EULER_WALL ) ||
7373  (Boundary == HEAT_FLUX ) ||
7374  (Boundary == ISOTHERMAL ) ||
7375  (Boundary == NEARFIELD_BOUNDARY)) {
7376  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->GetnVertex(iMarker); iVertex++) {
7377 
7378  /*--- The Pressure file uses the global numbering ---*/
7379 
7380 #ifndef HAVE_MPI
7381  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
7382 #else
7383  iPoint = geometry->node[geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode()]->GetGlobalIndex();
7384 #endif
7385 
7386  if (geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode() < geometry->GetnPointDomain()) {
7387  Point2Vertex[iPoint][0] = iMarker;
7388  Point2Vertex[iPoint][1] = iVertex;
7389  PointInDomain[iPoint] = true;
7390  solver_container->SetCPressureTarget(iMarker, iVertex, 0.0);
7391  }
7392 
7393  }
7394  }
7395  }
7396 
7397  /*--- Prepare to read the surface pressure files (CSV) ---*/
7398 
7399  surfCp_filename = "TargetCp";
7400  strcpy (cstr, surfCp_filename.c_str());
7401 
7402  /*--- Write file name with extension if unsteady or steady ---*/
7403 
7404  if ((config->GetUnsteady_Simulation() && config->GetWrt_Unsteady()) ||
7405  (config->GetUnsteady_Simulation() == TIME_SPECTRAL)) {
7406  if ((SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter) >= 0) && (SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter) < 10)) SPRINTF (buffer, "_0000%d.dat", SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter));
7407  if ((SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter) >= 10) && (SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter) < 100)) SPRINTF (buffer, "_000%d.dat", SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter));
7408  if ((SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter) >= 100) && (SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter) < 1000)) SPRINTF (buffer, "_00%d.dat", SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter));
7409  if ((SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter) >= 1000) && (SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter) < 10000)) SPRINTF (buffer, "_0%d.dat", SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter));
7410  if (SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter) >= 10000) SPRINTF (buffer, "_%d.dat", SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter));
7411  }
7412  else
7413  SPRINTF (buffer, ".dat");
7414 
7415  strcat (cstr, buffer);
7416 
7417  /*--- Read the surface pressure file ---*/
7418 
7419  string::size_type position;
7420 
7421  Surface_file.open(cstr, ios::in);
7422 
7423  if (!(Surface_file.fail())) {
7424 
7425  getline(Surface_file, text_line);
7426 
7427  while (getline(Surface_file, text_line)) {
7428  for (icommas = 0; icommas < 50; icommas++) {
7429  position = text_line.find( ",", 0 );
7430  if (position!=string::npos) text_line.erase (position,1);
7431  }
7432  stringstream point_line(text_line);
7433 
7434  if (geometry->GetnDim() == 2) point_line >> iPoint >> XCoord >> YCoord >> Pressure >> PressureCoeff;
7435  if (geometry->GetnDim() == 3) point_line >> iPoint >> XCoord >> YCoord >> ZCoord >> Pressure >> PressureCoeff;
7436 
7437  if (PointInDomain[iPoint]) {
7438 
7439  /*--- Find the vertex for the Point and Marker ---*/
7440 
7441  iMarker = Point2Vertex[iPoint][0];
7442  iVertex = Point2Vertex[iPoint][1];
7443 
7444  solver_container->SetCPressureTarget(iMarker, iVertex, PressureCoeff);
7445 
7446  }
7447 
7448  }
7449 
7450  Surface_file.close();
7451 
7452  }
7453 
7454  /*--- Compute the pressure difference ---*/
7455 
7456  PressDiff = 0.0;
7457  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
7458  Boundary = config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker);
7459 
7460  if ((Boundary == EULER_WALL ) ||
7461  (Boundary == HEAT_FLUX ) ||
7462  (Boundary == ISOTHERMAL ) ||
7463  (Boundary == NEARFIELD_BOUNDARY)) {
7464  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->GetnVertex(iMarker); iVertex++) {
7465 
7466  Normal = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal();
7467 
7468  Cp = solver_container->GetCPressure(iMarker, iVertex);
7469  CpTarget = solver_container->GetCPressureTarget(iMarker, iVertex);
7470 
7471  Area = 0.0;
7472  for (iDim = 0; iDim < geometry->GetnDim(); iDim++)
7473  Area += Normal[iDim]*Normal[iDim];
7474  Area = sqrt(Area);
7475 
7476  PressDiff += Area * (CpTarget - Cp) * (CpTarget - Cp);
7477  }
7478 
7479  }
7480  }
7481 
7482 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
7483  su2double MyPressDiff = PressDiff; PressDiff = 0.0;
7484  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&MyPressDiff, &PressDiff, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
7485 #endif
7486 
7487  /*--- Update the total Cp difference coeffient ---*/
7488 
7489  solver_container->SetTotal_CpDiff(PressDiff);
7490 
7491  delete [] Point2Vertex;
7492  delete [] PointInDomain;
7493 
7494 }

7501  Pressure, Cf;

7559  if ((SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter) >= 100) && (SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter) < 1000)) SPRINTF (buffer, "_00%d.dat", SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter));
7560  if ((SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter) >= 1000) && (SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter) < 10000)) SPRINTF (buffer, "_0%d.dat", SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter));
7561  if (SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter) >= 10000) SPRINTF (buffer, "_%d.dat", SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter));

7596

7598

7600 
7601  Surface_file.close();

7608  Boundary = config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker);

7611  (Boundary == HEAT_FLUX ) ||

7627 
7628  }
7629 
7630  }
7631  }

7636 #endif

7644

7647 void COutput::SetEquivalentArea(CSolver *solver_container, CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config, unsigned long iExtIter) {
7648 
7649  ofstream EquivArea_file, FuncGrad_file;
7650  unsigned short iMarker = 0, iDim;
7651  short *AzimuthalAngle = NULL;
7652  su2double Gamma, auxXCoord, auxYCoord, auxZCoord, InverseDesign = 0.0, DeltaX, Coord_i, Coord_j, jp1Coord, *Coord = NULL, MeanFuntion,
7653  *Face_Normal = NULL, auxArea, auxPress, Mach, Beta, R_Plane, Pressure_Inf,
7654  ModVelocity_Inf, Velocity_Inf[3], factor, *Xcoord = NULL, *Ycoord = NULL, *Zcoord = NULL,
7655  *Pressure = NULL, *FaceArea = NULL, *EquivArea = NULL, *TargetArea = NULL, *NearFieldWeight = NULL,
7656  *Weight = NULL, jFunction, jp1Function;
7657  unsigned long jVertex, iVertex, iPoint, nVertex_NearField = 0, auxPoint,
7658  *IdPoint = NULL, *IdDomain = NULL, auxDomain;
7659  unsigned short iPhiAngle;
7660  ofstream NearFieldEA_file; ifstream TargetEA_file;
7661 
7662  su2double XCoordBegin_OF = config->GetEA_IntLimit(0);
7663  su2double XCoordEnd_OF = config->GetEA_IntLimit(1);
7664 
7665  unsigned short nDim = geometry->GetnDim();
7666  su2double AoA = -(config->GetAoA()*PI_NUMBER/180.0);
7667  su2double EAScaleFactor = config->GetEA_ScaleFactor(); // The EA Obj. Func. should be ~ force based Obj. Func.
7668 
7669  int rank = MESH_0;
7670 
7671  Mach = config->GetMach();
7672  Gamma = config->GetGamma();
7673  Beta = sqrt(Mach*Mach-1.0);
7674  R_Plane = fabs(config->GetEA_IntLimit(2));
7675  Pressure_Inf = config->GetPressure_FreeStreamND();
7676  Velocity_Inf[0] = config->GetVelocity_FreeStreamND()[0];
7677  Velocity_Inf[1] = config->GetVelocity_FreeStreamND()[1];
7678  Velocity_Inf[2] = config->GetVelocity_FreeStreamND()[2];
7679  ModVelocity_Inf = 0;
7680  for (iDim = 0; iDim < 3; iDim++)
7681  ModVelocity_Inf += Velocity_Inf[iDim] * Velocity_Inf[iDim];
7682 
7683  factor = 4.0*sqrt(2.0*Beta*R_Plane) / (Gamma*Pressure_Inf*Mach*Mach);
7684 
7685 #ifndef HAVE_MPI
7686 
7687  /*--- Compute the total number of points on the near-field ---*/
7688 
7689  nVertex_NearField = 0;
7690  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++)
7691  if (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == NEARFIELD_BOUNDARY)
7692  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->GetnVertex(iMarker); iVertex++) {
7693  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
7694  Face_Normal = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal();
7695  Coord = geometry->node[iPoint]->GetCoord();
7696 
7697  /*--- Using Face_Normal(z), and Coord(z) we identify only a surface,
7698  note that there are 2 NEARFIELD_BOUNDARY surfaces ---*/
7699 
7700  if ((Face_Normal[nDim-1] > 0.0) && (Coord[nDim-1] < 0.0)) nVertex_NearField ++;
7701  }
7702 
7703  /*--- Create an array with all the coordinates, points, pressures, face area,
7704  equivalent area, and nearfield weight ---*/
7705 
7706  Xcoord = new su2double[nVertex_NearField];
7707  Ycoord = new su2double[nVertex_NearField];
7708  Zcoord = new su2double[nVertex_NearField];
7709  AzimuthalAngle = new short[nVertex_NearField];
7710  IdPoint = new unsigned long[nVertex_NearField];
7711  IdDomain = new unsigned long[nVertex_NearField];
7712  Pressure = new su2double[nVertex_NearField];
7713  FaceArea = new su2double[nVertex_NearField];
7714  EquivArea = new su2double[nVertex_NearField];
7715  TargetArea = new su2double[nVertex_NearField];
7716  NearFieldWeight = new su2double[nVertex_NearField];
7717  Weight = new su2double[nVertex_NearField];
7718 
7719  /*--- Copy the boundary information to an array ---*/
7720 
7721  nVertex_NearField = 0;
7722  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++)
7723  if (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == NEARFIELD_BOUNDARY)
7724  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->GetnVertex(iMarker); iVertex++) {
7725  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
7726  Face_Normal = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal();
7727  Coord = geometry->node[iPoint]->GetCoord();
7728 
7729  if ((Face_Normal[nDim-1] > 0.0) && (Coord[nDim-1] < 0.0)) {
7730 
7731  IdPoint[nVertex_NearField] = iPoint;
7732  Xcoord[nVertex_NearField] = geometry->node[iPoint]->GetCoord(0);
7733  Ycoord[nVertex_NearField] = geometry->node[iPoint]->GetCoord(1);
7734 
7735  if (nDim ==2) {
7736  AzimuthalAngle[nVertex_NearField] = 0;
7737  }
7738 
7739  if (nDim == 3) {
7740  Zcoord[nVertex_NearField] = geometry->node[iPoint]->GetCoord(2);
7741 
7742  /*--- Rotate the nearfield cylinder (AoA) only 3D ---*/
7743 
7744  su2double YcoordRot = Ycoord[nVertex_NearField];
7745  su2double ZcoordRot = Xcoord[nVertex_NearField]*sin(AoA) + Zcoord[nVertex_NearField]*cos(AoA);
7746 
7747  /*--- Compute the Azimuthal angle (resolution of degress in the Azimuthal angle)---*/
7748 
7749  su2double AngleDouble; short AngleInt;
7750  AngleDouble = fabs(atan(-YcoordRot/ZcoordRot)*180.0/PI_NUMBER);
7751 
7752  /*--- Fix an azimuthal line due to misalignments of the near-field ---*/
7753 
7754  su2double FixAzimuthalLine = config->GetFixAzimuthalLine();
7755 
7756  if ((AngleDouble >= FixAzimuthalLine - 0.1) && (AngleDouble <= FixAzimuthalLine + 0.1)) AngleDouble = FixAzimuthalLine - 0.1;
7757 
7758  AngleInt = SU2_TYPE::Short(floor(AngleDouble + 0.5));
7759  if (AngleInt >= 0) AzimuthalAngle[nVertex_NearField] = AngleInt;
7760  else AzimuthalAngle[nVertex_NearField] = 180 + AngleInt;
7761  }
7762 
7763  if (AzimuthalAngle[nVertex_NearField] <= 60) {
7764  Pressure[nVertex_NearField] = solver_container->node[iPoint]->GetPressure();
7765  FaceArea[nVertex_NearField] = fabs(Face_Normal[nDim-1]);
7766  nVertex_NearField ++;
7767  }
7768 
7769  }
7770  }
7771 
7772 #else
7773 
7774  int nProcessor;
7775  MPI_Comm_size(MPI_COMM_WORLD, &nProcessor);
7776  MPI_Comm_rank(MPI_COMM_WORLD, &rank);
7777 
7778  unsigned long nLocalVertex_NearField = 0, MaxLocalVertex_NearField = 0;
7779  int iProcessor;
7780 
7781  unsigned long *Buffer_Receive_nVertex = NULL;
7782  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) {
7783  Buffer_Receive_nVertex = new unsigned long [nProcessor];
7784  }
7785 
7786  /*--- Compute the total number of points of the near-field ghost nodes ---*/
7787 
7788  nLocalVertex_NearField = 0;
7789  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++)
7790  if (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == NEARFIELD_BOUNDARY)
7791  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->GetnVertex(iMarker); iVertex++) {
7792  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
7793  Face_Normal = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal();
7794  Coord = geometry->node[iPoint]->GetCoord();
7795 
7796  if (geometry->node[iPoint]->GetDomain())
7797  if ((Face_Normal[nDim-1] > 0.0) && (Coord[nDim-1] < 0.0))
7798  nLocalVertex_NearField ++;
7799  }
7800 
7801  unsigned long *Buffer_Send_nVertex = new unsigned long [1];
7802  Buffer_Send_nVertex[0] = nLocalVertex_NearField;
7803 
7804  /*--- Send Near-Field vertex information --*/
7805 
7806  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&nLocalVertex_NearField, &nVertex_NearField, 1, MPI_UNSIGNED_LONG, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
7807  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&nLocalVertex_NearField, &MaxLocalVertex_NearField, 1, MPI_UNSIGNED_LONG, MPI_MAX, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
7808  SU2_MPI::Gather(Buffer_Send_nVertex, 1, MPI_UNSIGNED_LONG, Buffer_Receive_nVertex, 1, MPI_UNSIGNED_LONG, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
7809  delete [] Buffer_Send_nVertex;
7810 
7811  su2double *Buffer_Send_Xcoord = new su2double[MaxLocalVertex_NearField];
7812  su2double *Buffer_Send_Ycoord = new su2double[MaxLocalVertex_NearField];
7813  su2double *Buffer_Send_Zcoord = new su2double[MaxLocalVertex_NearField];
7814  unsigned long *Buffer_Send_IdPoint = new unsigned long [MaxLocalVertex_NearField];
7815  su2double *Buffer_Send_Pressure = new su2double [MaxLocalVertex_NearField];
7816  su2double *Buffer_Send_FaceArea = new su2double[MaxLocalVertex_NearField];
7817 
7818  su2double *Buffer_Receive_Xcoord = NULL;
7819  su2double *Buffer_Receive_Ycoord = NULL;
7820  su2double *Buffer_Receive_Zcoord = NULL;
7821  unsigned long *Buffer_Receive_IdPoint = NULL;
7822  su2double *Buffer_Receive_Pressure = NULL;
7823  su2double *Buffer_Receive_FaceArea = NULL;
7824 
7825  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) {
7826  Buffer_Receive_Xcoord = new su2double[nProcessor*MaxLocalVertex_NearField];
7827  Buffer_Receive_Ycoord = new su2double[nProcessor*MaxLocalVertex_NearField];
7828  Buffer_Receive_Zcoord = new su2double[nProcessor*MaxLocalVertex_NearField];
7829  Buffer_Receive_IdPoint = new unsigned long[nProcessor*MaxLocalVertex_NearField];
7830  Buffer_Receive_Pressure = new su2double[nProcessor*MaxLocalVertex_NearField];
7831  Buffer_Receive_FaceArea = new su2double[nProcessor*MaxLocalVertex_NearField];
7832  }
7833 
7834  unsigned long nBuffer_Xcoord = MaxLocalVertex_NearField;
7835  unsigned long nBuffer_Ycoord = MaxLocalVertex_NearField;
7836  unsigned long nBuffer_Zcoord = MaxLocalVertex_NearField;
7837  unsigned long nBuffer_IdPoint = MaxLocalVertex_NearField;
7838  unsigned long nBuffer_Pressure = MaxLocalVertex_NearField;
7839  unsigned long nBuffer_FaceArea = MaxLocalVertex_NearField;
7840 
7841  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < MaxLocalVertex_NearField; iVertex++) {
7842  Buffer_Send_IdPoint[iVertex] = 0; Buffer_Send_Pressure[iVertex] = 0.0;
7843  Buffer_Send_FaceArea[iVertex] = 0.0; Buffer_Send_Xcoord[iVertex] = 0.0;
7844  Buffer_Send_Ycoord[iVertex] = 0.0; Buffer_Send_Zcoord[iVertex] = 0.0;
7845  }
7846 
7847  /*--- Copy coordinates, index points, and pressures to the auxiliar vector --*/
7848 
7849  nLocalVertex_NearField = 0;
7850  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++)
7851  if (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == NEARFIELD_BOUNDARY)
7852  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->GetnVertex(iMarker); iVertex++) {
7853  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
7854  Face_Normal = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal();
7855  Coord = geometry->node[iPoint]->GetCoord();
7856 
7857  if (geometry->node[iPoint]->GetDomain())
7858  if ((Face_Normal[nDim-1] > 0.0) && (Coord[nDim-1] < 0.0)) {
7859  Buffer_Send_IdPoint[nLocalVertex_NearField] = iPoint;
7860  Buffer_Send_Xcoord[nLocalVertex_NearField] = geometry->node[iPoint]->GetCoord(0);
7861  Buffer_Send_Ycoord[nLocalVertex_NearField] = geometry->node[iPoint]->GetCoord(1);
7862  Buffer_Send_Zcoord[nLocalVertex_NearField] = geometry->node[iPoint]->GetCoord(2);
7863  Buffer_Send_Pressure[nLocalVertex_NearField] = solver_container->node[iPoint]->GetPressure();
7864  Buffer_Send_FaceArea[nLocalVertex_NearField] = fabs(Face_Normal[nDim-1]);
7865  nLocalVertex_NearField++;
7866  }
7867  }
7868 
7869  /*--- Send all the information --*/
7870 
7871  SU2_MPI::Gather(Buffer_Send_Xcoord, nBuffer_Xcoord, MPI_DOUBLE, Buffer_Receive_Xcoord, nBuffer_Xcoord, MPI_DOUBLE, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
7872  SU2_MPI::Gather(Buffer_Send_Ycoord, nBuffer_Ycoord, MPI_DOUBLE, Buffer_Receive_Ycoord, nBuffer_Ycoord, MPI_DOUBLE, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
7873  SU2_MPI::Gather(Buffer_Send_Zcoord, nBuffer_Zcoord, MPI_DOUBLE, Buffer_Receive_Zcoord, nBuffer_Zcoord, MPI_DOUBLE, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
7874  SU2_MPI::Gather(Buffer_Send_IdPoint, nBuffer_IdPoint, MPI_UNSIGNED_LONG, Buffer_Receive_IdPoint, nBuffer_IdPoint, MPI_UNSIGNED_LONG, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
7875  SU2_MPI::Gather(Buffer_Send_Pressure, nBuffer_Pressure, MPI_DOUBLE, Buffer_Receive_Pressure, nBuffer_Pressure, MPI_DOUBLE, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
7876  SU2_MPI::Gather(Buffer_Send_FaceArea, nBuffer_FaceArea, MPI_DOUBLE, Buffer_Receive_FaceArea, nBuffer_FaceArea, MPI_DOUBLE, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
7877  delete [] Buffer_Send_Xcoord;
7878  delete [] Buffer_Send_Ycoord;
7879  delete [] Buffer_Send_Zcoord;
7880  delete [] Buffer_Send_IdPoint;
7881  delete [] Buffer_Send_Pressure;
7882  delete [] Buffer_Send_FaceArea;
7883 
7884  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) {
7885 
7886  Xcoord = new su2double[nVertex_NearField];
7887  Ycoord = new su2double[nVertex_NearField];
7888  Zcoord = new su2double[nVertex_NearField];
7889  AzimuthalAngle = new short[nVertex_NearField];
7890  IdPoint = new unsigned long[nVertex_NearField];
7891  IdDomain = new unsigned long[nVertex_NearField];
7892  Pressure = new su2double[nVertex_NearField];
7893  FaceArea = new su2double[nVertex_NearField];
7894  EquivArea = new su2double[nVertex_NearField];
7895  TargetArea = new su2double[nVertex_NearField];
7896  NearFieldWeight = new su2double[nVertex_NearField];
7897  Weight = new su2double[nVertex_NearField];
7898 
7899  nVertex_NearField = 0;
7900  for (iProcessor = 0; iProcessor < nProcessor; iProcessor++)
7901  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < Buffer_Receive_nVertex[iProcessor]; iVertex++) {
7902  Xcoord[nVertex_NearField] = Buffer_Receive_Xcoord[iProcessor*MaxLocalVertex_NearField+iVertex];
7903  Ycoord[nVertex_NearField] = Buffer_Receive_Ycoord[iProcessor*MaxLocalVertex_NearField+iVertex];
7904 
7905  if (nDim == 2) {
7906  AzimuthalAngle[nVertex_NearField] = 0;
7907  }
7908 
7909  if (nDim == 3) {
7910  Zcoord[nVertex_NearField] = Buffer_Receive_Zcoord[iProcessor*MaxLocalVertex_NearField+iVertex];
7911 
7912  /*--- Rotate the nearfield cylinder ---*/
7913 
7914  su2double YcoordRot = Ycoord[nVertex_NearField];
7915  su2double ZcoordRot = Xcoord[nVertex_NearField]*sin(AoA) + Zcoord[nVertex_NearField]*cos(AoA);
7916 
7917  /*--- Compute the Azimuthal angle ---*/
7918 
7919  su2double AngleDouble; short AngleInt;
7920  AngleDouble = fabs(atan(-YcoordRot/ZcoordRot)*180.0/PI_NUMBER);
7921 
7922  /*--- Fix an azimuthal line due to misalignments of the near-field ---*/
7923 
7924  su2double FixAzimuthalLine = config->GetFixAzimuthalLine();
7925 
7926  if ((AngleDouble >= FixAzimuthalLine - 0.1) && (AngleDouble <= FixAzimuthalLine + 0.1))
7927  AngleDouble = FixAzimuthalLine - 0.1;
7928 
7929  AngleInt = SU2_TYPE::Short(floor(AngleDouble + 0.5));
7930 
7931  if (AngleInt >= 0) AzimuthalAngle[nVertex_NearField] = AngleInt;
7932  else AzimuthalAngle[nVertex_NearField] = 180 + AngleInt;
7933  }
7934 
7935  if (AzimuthalAngle[nVertex_NearField] <= 60) {
7936  IdPoint[nVertex_NearField] = Buffer_Receive_IdPoint[iProcessor*MaxLocalVertex_NearField+iVertex];
7937  Pressure[nVertex_NearField] = Buffer_Receive_Pressure[iProcessor*MaxLocalVertex_NearField+iVertex];
7938  FaceArea[nVertex_NearField] = Buffer_Receive_FaceArea[iProcessor*MaxLocalVertex_NearField+iVertex];
7939  IdDomain[nVertex_NearField] = iProcessor;
7940  nVertex_NearField++;
7941  }
7942 
7943  }
7944 
7945  delete [] Buffer_Receive_nVertex;
7946 
7947  delete [] Buffer_Receive_Xcoord;
7948  delete [] Buffer_Receive_Ycoord;
7949  delete [] Buffer_Receive_Zcoord;
7950  delete [] Buffer_Receive_IdPoint;
7951  delete [] Buffer_Receive_Pressure;
7952  delete [] Buffer_Receive_FaceArea;
7953 
7954  }
7955 
7956 #endif
7957 
7958  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) {
7959 
7960  vector<short> PhiAngleList;
7961  vector<short>::iterator IterPhiAngleList;
7962 
7963  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < nVertex_NearField; iVertex++)
7964  PhiAngleList.push_back(AzimuthalAngle[iVertex]);
7965 
7966  sort( PhiAngleList.begin(), PhiAngleList.end());
7967  IterPhiAngleList = unique( PhiAngleList.begin(), PhiAngleList.end());
7968  PhiAngleList.resize( IterPhiAngleList - PhiAngleList.begin() );
7969 
7970  /*--- Create vectors and distribute the values among the different PhiAngle queues ---*/
7971 
7972  vector<vector<su2double> > Xcoord_PhiAngle; Xcoord_PhiAngle.resize(PhiAngleList.size());
7973  vector<vector<su2double> > Ycoord_PhiAngle; Ycoord_PhiAngle.resize(PhiAngleList.size());
7974  vector<vector<su2double> > Zcoord_PhiAngle; Zcoord_PhiAngle.resize(PhiAngleList.size());
7975  vector<vector<unsigned long> > IdPoint_PhiAngle; IdPoint_PhiAngle.resize(PhiAngleList.size());
7976  vector<vector<unsigned long> > IdDomain_PhiAngle; IdDomain_PhiAngle.resize(PhiAngleList.size());
7977  vector<vector<su2double> > Pressure_PhiAngle; Pressure_PhiAngle.resize(PhiAngleList.size());
7978  vector<vector<su2double> > FaceArea_PhiAngle; FaceArea_PhiAngle.resize(PhiAngleList.size());
7979  vector<vector<su2double> > EquivArea_PhiAngle; EquivArea_PhiAngle.resize(PhiAngleList.size());
7980  vector<vector<su2double> > TargetArea_PhiAngle; TargetArea_PhiAngle.resize(PhiAngleList.size());
7981  vector<vector<su2double> > NearFieldWeight_PhiAngle; NearFieldWeight_PhiAngle.resize(PhiAngleList.size());
7982  vector<vector<su2double> > Weight_PhiAngle; Weight_PhiAngle.resize(PhiAngleList.size());
7983 
7984  /*--- Distribute the values among the different PhiAngles ---*/
7985 
7986  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < nVertex_NearField; iVertex++)
7987  for (iPhiAngle = 0; iPhiAngle < PhiAngleList.size(); iPhiAngle++)
7988  if (AzimuthalAngle[iVertex] == PhiAngleList[iPhiAngle]) {
7989  Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].push_back(Xcoord[iVertex]);
7990  Ycoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].push_back(Ycoord[iVertex]);
7991  Zcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].push_back(Zcoord[iVertex]);
7992  IdPoint_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].push_back(IdPoint[iVertex]);
7993  IdDomain_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].push_back(IdDomain[iVertex]);
7994  Pressure_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].push_back(Pressure[iVertex]);
7995  FaceArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].push_back(FaceArea[iVertex]);
7996  EquivArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].push_back(EquivArea[iVertex]);
7997  TargetArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].push_back(TargetArea[iVertex]);
7998  NearFieldWeight_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].push_back(NearFieldWeight[iVertex]);
7999  Weight_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].push_back(Weight[iVertex]);
8000  }
8001 
8002  /*--- Order the arrays (x Coordinate, Pressure, Point, and Domain) ---*/
8003 
8004  for (iPhiAngle = 0; iPhiAngle < PhiAngleList.size(); iPhiAngle++)
8005  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].size(); iVertex++)
8006  for (jVertex = 0; jVertex < Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].size() - 1 - iVertex; jVertex++)
8007  if (Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex] > Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1]) {
8008  auxXCoord = Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex]; Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex] = Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1]; Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1] = auxXCoord;
8009  auxYCoord = Ycoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex]; Ycoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex] = Ycoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1]; Ycoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1] = auxYCoord;
8010  auxZCoord = Zcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex]; Zcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex] = Zcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1]; Zcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1] = auxZCoord;
8011  auxPress = Pressure_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex]; Pressure_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex] = Pressure_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1]; Pressure_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1] = auxPress;
8012  auxArea = FaceArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex]; FaceArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex] = FaceArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1]; FaceArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1] = auxArea;
8013  auxPoint = IdPoint_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex]; IdPoint_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex] = IdPoint_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1]; IdPoint_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1] = auxPoint;
8014  auxDomain = IdDomain_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex]; IdDomain_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex] = IdDomain_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1]; IdDomain_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1] = auxDomain;
8015  }
8016 
8017 
8018  /*--- Check that all the azimuth lists have the same size ---*/
8019 
8020  unsigned short nVertex = Xcoord_PhiAngle[0].size();
8021  for (iPhiAngle = 0; iPhiAngle < PhiAngleList.size(); iPhiAngle++) {
8022  unsigned short nVertex_aux = Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].size();
8023  if (nVertex_aux != nVertex) cout <<"Be careful!!! one azimuth list is shorter than the other"<< endl;
8024  nVertex = min(nVertex, nVertex_aux);
8025  }
8026 
8027  /*--- Compute equivalent area distribution at each azimuth angle ---*/
8028 
8029  for (iPhiAngle = 0; iPhiAngle < PhiAngleList.size(); iPhiAngle++) {
8030  EquivArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][0] = 0.0;
8031  for (iVertex = 1; iVertex < EquivArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].size(); iVertex++) {
8032  EquivArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex] = 0.0;
8033 
8034  Coord_i = Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex]*cos(AoA) - Zcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex]*sin(AoA);
8035 
8036  for (jVertex = 0; jVertex < iVertex-1; jVertex++) {
8037 
8038  Coord_j = Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex]*cos(AoA) - Zcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex]*sin(AoA);
8039  jp1Coord = Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1]*cos(AoA) - Zcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1]*sin(AoA);
8040 
8041  jFunction = factor*(Pressure_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex] - Pressure_Inf)*sqrt(Coord_i-Coord_j);
8042  jp1Function = factor*(Pressure_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1] - Pressure_Inf)*sqrt(Coord_i-jp1Coord);
8043 
8044  DeltaX = (jp1Coord-Coord_j);
8045  MeanFuntion = 0.5*(jp1Function + jFunction);
8046  EquivArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex] += DeltaX * MeanFuntion;
8047  }
8048  }
8049  }
8050 
8051  /*--- Create a file with the equivalent area distribution at each azimuthal angle ---*/
8052 
8053  NearFieldEA_file.precision(15);
8054  NearFieldEA_file.open("Equivalent_Area.dat", ios::out);
8055  NearFieldEA_file << "TITLE = \"Equivalent Area evaluation at each azimuthal angle\"" << "\n";
8056 
8057  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US)
8058  NearFieldEA_file << "VARIABLES = \"Height (in) at r="<< R_Plane*12.0 << " in. (cyl. coord. system)\"";
8059  else
8060  NearFieldEA_file << "VARIABLES = \"Height (m) at r="<< R_Plane << " m. (cylindrical coordinate system)\"";
8061 
8062  for (iPhiAngle = 0; iPhiAngle < PhiAngleList.size(); iPhiAngle++) {
8063  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US)
8064  NearFieldEA_file << ", \"Equivalent Area (ft<sup>2</sup>), <greek>F</greek>= " << PhiAngleList[iPhiAngle] << " deg.\"";
8065  else
8066  NearFieldEA_file << ", \"Equivalent Area (m<sup>2</sup>), <greek>F</greek>= " << PhiAngleList[iPhiAngle] << " deg.\"";
8067  }
8068 
8069  NearFieldEA_file << "\n";
8070  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < EquivArea_PhiAngle[0].size(); iVertex++) {
8071 
8072  su2double XcoordRot = Xcoord_PhiAngle[0][iVertex]*cos(AoA) - Zcoord_PhiAngle[0][iVertex]*sin(AoA);
8073  su2double XcoordRot_init = Xcoord_PhiAngle[0][0]*cos(AoA) - Zcoord_PhiAngle[0][0]*sin(AoA);
8074 
8075  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US)
8076  NearFieldEA_file << scientific << (XcoordRot - XcoordRot_init) * 12.0;
8077  else
8078  NearFieldEA_file << scientific << (XcoordRot - XcoordRot_init);
8079 
8080  for (iPhiAngle = 0; iPhiAngle < PhiAngleList.size(); iPhiAngle++) {
8081  NearFieldEA_file << scientific << ", " << EquivArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex];
8082  }
8083 
8084  NearFieldEA_file << "\n";
8085 
8086  }
8087  NearFieldEA_file.close();
8088 
8089  /*--- Read target equivalent area from the configuration file,
8090  this first implementation requires a complete table (same as the original
8091  EA table). so... no interpolation. ---*/
8092 
8093  vector<vector<su2double> > TargetArea_PhiAngle_Trans;
8094  TargetEA_file.open("TargetEA.dat", ios::in);
8095 
8096  if (TargetEA_file.fail()) {
8097  if (iExtIter == 0) { cout << "There is no Target Equivalent Area file (TargetEA.dat)!!"<< endl;
8098  cout << "Using default parameters (Target Equiv Area = 0.0)" << endl;
8099  }
8100  /*--- Set the table to 0 ---*/
8101  for (iPhiAngle = 0; iPhiAngle < PhiAngleList.size(); iPhiAngle++)
8102  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < TargetArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].size(); iVertex++)
8103  TargetArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex] = 0.0;
8104  }
8105  else {
8106 
8107  /*--- skip header lines ---*/
8108 
8109  string line;
8110  getline(TargetEA_file, line);
8111  getline(TargetEA_file, line);
8112 
8113  while (TargetEA_file) {
8114 
8115  string line;
8116  getline(TargetEA_file, line);
8117  istringstream is(line);
8118  vector<su2double> row;
8119  unsigned short iter = 0;
8120 
8121  while (is.good()) {
8122  string token;
8123  getline(is, token,',');
8124 
8125  istringstream js(token);
8126 
8127  su2double data;
8128  js >> data;
8129 
8130  /*--- The first element in the table is the coordinate (in or m)---*/
8131 
8132  if (iter != 0) row.push_back(data);
8133  iter++;
8134 
8135  }
8136  TargetArea_PhiAngle_Trans.push_back(row);
8137  }
8138 
8139  for (iPhiAngle = 0; iPhiAngle < PhiAngleList.size(); iPhiAngle++)
8140  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < EquivArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].size(); iVertex++)
8141  TargetArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex] = TargetArea_PhiAngle_Trans[iVertex][iPhiAngle];
8142 
8143  }
8144 
8145  /*--- Divide by the number of Phi angles in the nearfield ---*/
8146 
8147  su2double PhiFactor = 1.0/su2double(PhiAngleList.size());
8148 
8149  /*--- Evaluate the objective function ---*/
8150 
8151  InverseDesign = 0;
8152  for (iPhiAngle = 0; iPhiAngle < PhiAngleList.size(); iPhiAngle++)
8153  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < EquivArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].size(); iVertex++) {
8154  Weight_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex] = 1.0;
8155  Coord_i = Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex];
8156 
8157  su2double Difference = EquivArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex]-TargetArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex];
8158  su2double percentage = fabs(Difference)*100/fabs(TargetArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex]);
8159 
8160  if ((percentage < 0.1) || (Coord_i < XCoordBegin_OF) || (Coord_i > XCoordEnd_OF)) Difference = 0.0;
8161 
8162  InverseDesign += EAScaleFactor*PhiFactor*Weight_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex]*Difference*Difference;
8163 
8164  }
8165 
8166  /*--- Evaluate the weight of the nearfield pressure (adjoint input) ---*/
8167 
8168  for (iPhiAngle = 0; iPhiAngle < PhiAngleList.size(); iPhiAngle++)
8169  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < EquivArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].size(); iVertex++) {
8170  Coord_i = Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex];
8171  NearFieldWeight_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex] = 0.0;
8172  for (jVertex = iVertex; jVertex < EquivArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].size(); jVertex++) {
8173  Coord_j = Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex];
8174  Weight_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex] = 1.0;
8175 
8176  su2double Difference = EquivArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex]-TargetArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex];
8177  su2double percentage = fabs(Difference)*100/fabs(TargetArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex]);
8178 
8179  if ((percentage < 0.1) || (Coord_j < XCoordBegin_OF) || (Coord_j > XCoordEnd_OF)) Difference = 0.0;
8180 
8181  NearFieldWeight_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex] += EAScaleFactor*PhiFactor*Weight_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex]*2.0*Difference*factor*sqrt(Coord_j-Coord_i);
8182  }
8183  }
8184 
8185  /*--- Write the Nearfield pressure at each Azimuthal PhiAngle ---*/
8186 
8187  EquivArea_file.precision(15);
8188  EquivArea_file.open("nearfield_flow.dat", ios::out);
8189  EquivArea_file << "TITLE = \"Equivalent Area evaluation at each azimuthal angle\"" << "\n";
8190 
8191  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US)
8192  EquivArea_file << "VARIABLES = \"Height (in) at r="<< R_Plane*12.0 << " in. (cyl. coord. system)\",\"Equivalent Area (ft<sup>2</sup>)\",\"Target Equivalent Area (ft<sup>2</sup>)\",\"Cp\"" << "\n";
8193  else
8194  EquivArea_file << "VARIABLES = \"Height (m) at r="<< R_Plane << " m. (cylindrical coordinate system)\",\"Equivalent Area (m<sup>2</sup>)\",\"Target Equivalent Area (m<sup>2</sup>)\",\"Cp\"" << "\n";
8195 
8196  for (iPhiAngle = 0; iPhiAngle < PhiAngleList.size(); iPhiAngle++) {
8197  EquivArea_file << fixed << "ZONE T= \"<greek>F</greek>=" << PhiAngleList[iPhiAngle] << " deg.\"" << "\n";
8198  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].size(); iVertex++) {
8199 
8200  su2double XcoordRot = Xcoord_PhiAngle[0][iVertex]*cos(AoA) - Zcoord_PhiAngle[0][iVertex]*sin(AoA);
8201  su2double XcoordRot_init = Xcoord_PhiAngle[0][0]*cos(AoA) - Zcoord_PhiAngle[0][0]*sin(AoA);
8202 
8203  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US)
8204  EquivArea_file << scientific << (XcoordRot - XcoordRot_init) * 12.0;
8205  else
8206  EquivArea_file << scientific << (XcoordRot - XcoordRot_init);
8207 
8208  EquivArea_file << scientific << ", " << EquivArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex]
8209  << ", " << TargetArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex] << ", " << (Pressure_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex]-Pressure_Inf)/Pressure_Inf << "\n";
8210  }
8211  }
8212 
8213  EquivArea_file.close();
8214 
8215  /*--- Write Weight file for adjoint computation ---*/
8216 
8217  FuncGrad_file.precision(15);
8218  FuncGrad_file.open("WeightNF.dat", ios::out);
8219 
8220  FuncGrad_file << scientific << "-1.0";
8221  for (iPhiAngle = 0; iPhiAngle < PhiAngleList.size(); iPhiAngle++)
8222  FuncGrad_file << scientific << "\t" << PhiAngleList[iPhiAngle];
8223  FuncGrad_file << "\n";
8224 
8225  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < NearFieldWeight_PhiAngle[0].size(); iVertex++) {
8226  su2double XcoordRot = Xcoord_PhiAngle[0][iVertex]*cos(AoA) - Zcoord_PhiAngle[0][iVertex]*sin(AoA);
8227  FuncGrad_file << scientific << XcoordRot;
8228  for (iPhiAngle = 0; iPhiAngle < PhiAngleList.size(); iPhiAngle++)
8229  FuncGrad_file << scientific << "\t" << NearFieldWeight_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex];
8230  FuncGrad_file << "\n";
8231  }
8232  FuncGrad_file.close();
8233 
8234  /*--- Delete structures ---*/
8235 
8236  delete [] Xcoord; delete [] Ycoord; delete [] Zcoord;
8237  delete [] AzimuthalAngle; delete [] IdPoint; delete [] IdDomain;
8238  delete [] Pressure; delete [] FaceArea;
8239  delete [] EquivArea; delete [] TargetArea;
8240  delete [] NearFieldWeight; delete [] Weight;
8241 
8242  }
8243 
8244 #ifndef HAVE_MPI
8245 
8246  /*--- Store the value of the NearField coefficient ---*/
8247 
8248  solver_container->SetTotal_CEquivArea(InverseDesign);
8249 
8250 #else
8251 
8252  /*--- Send the value of the NearField coefficient to all the processors ---*/
8253 
8254  SU2_MPI::Bcast(&InverseDesign, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
8255 
8256  /*--- Store the value of the NearField coefficient ---*/
8257 
8258  solver_container->SetTotal_CEquivArea(InverseDesign);
8259 
8260 #endif
8261 
8262 }
8263 
8264 void COutput::SetSensitivity_Files(CGeometry **geometry, CConfig **config, unsigned short val_nZone){
8265 
8266  unsigned short iMarker,iDim, nDim, iVar, nMarker, nVar;
8267  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint, nPoint, nVertex;
8268  su2double *Normal, Prod, Sens = 0.0, SensDim, Area;
8269 
8270  unsigned short iZone;
8271 
8272  CSolver **solver = new CSolver*[val_nZone];
8273 
8274  for (iZone = 0; iZone < val_nZone; iZone++) {
8275 
8276 
8277  nPoint = geometry[iZone]->GetnPoint();
8278  nDim = geometry[iZone]->GetnDim();
8279  nMarker = config[iZone]->GetnMarker_All();
8280  nVar = nDim + 1;
8281 
8282  /* --- We create a baseline solver to easily merge the sensitivity information --- */
8283 
8284  vector<string> fieldnames;
8285  fieldnames.push_back("\"Point\",");
8286  fieldnames.push_back("\"x\",");
8287  fieldnames.push_back("\"y\",");
8288  if (nDim == 3){
8289  fieldnames.push_back("\"z\",");
8290  }
8291  fieldnames.push_back("\"Sensitivity_x\",");
8292  fieldnames.push_back("\"Sensitivity_y\",");
8293  if (nDim == 3){
8294  fieldnames.push_back("\"Sensitivity_z\",");
8295  }
8296  fieldnames.push_back("\"Sensitivity\"");
8297 
8298  solver[iZone] = new CBaselineSolver(geometry[iZone], config[iZone], nVar+nDim, fieldnames);
8299 
8300  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPoint; iPoint++){
8301  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++){
8302  solver[iZone]->node[iPoint]->SetSolution(iDim, geometry[iZone]->node[iPoint]->GetCoord(iDim));
8303  }
8304  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nDim; iVar++){
8305  solver[iZone]->node[iPoint]->SetSolution(iVar+nDim, geometry[iZone]->GetSensitivity(iPoint, iVar));
8306  }
8307  }
8308 
8309  /*--- Compute the sensitivity in normal direction ---*/
8310 
8311  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarker; iMarker++){
8312 
8313  if((config[iZone]->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == HEAT_FLUX ) ||
8314  (config[iZone]->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == EULER_WALL ) ||
8315  (config[iZone]->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ISOTHERMAL )){
8316 
8317  nVertex = geometry[iZone]->GetnVertex(iMarker);
8318 
8319  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < nVertex; iVertex++){
8320  iPoint = geometry[iZone]->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
8321  Normal = geometry[iZone]->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal();
8322  Prod = 0.0;
8323  Area = 0.0;
8324  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++){
8325 
8326  /*--- Retrieve the gradient calculated with discrete adjoint method --- */
8327 
8328  SensDim = geometry[iZone]->GetSensitivity(iPoint, iDim);
8329 
8330  /*--- Calculate scalar product for projection onto the normal vector ---*/
8331 
8332  Prod += Normal[iDim]*SensDim;
8333 
8334  Area += Normal[iDim]*Normal[iDim];
8335  }
8336 
8337  Area = sqrt(Area);
8338 
8339  /*--- Projection of the gradient onto the normal vector of the surface ---*/
8340 
8341  Sens = Prod/Area;
8342 
8343  solver[iZone]->node[iPoint]->SetSolution(2*nDim, Sens);
8344 
8345  }
8346  }
8347  }
8348  }
8349 
8350  /*--- Merge the information and write the output files ---*/
8351 
8352  SetBaselineResult_Files(solver,geometry, config, 0, val_nZone);
8353 
8354 }
8355
